NK033(gi)007:1: // rdzogs pa chen po rgyud bcu bdun gyi dbang chog
NK033(gi)007:2: rdzogs pa rang byung gi rgyud kyi dgongs don ji
NK033(gi)007:3: bzhin chog bsgrigs zin bris su bkod pa bzhugs so
NK033(gi)007:4: // na mo gu ru d+he wa d+h+aa ki n+ai sa pa ri w+aa r+aa ya /
NK033(gi)007:5: bla ma mchog dang kun bzang chos kyi sku //
NK033(gi)007:6: zhi khro rab 'byams dkyil 'khor kun gyi gtso //
NK033(gi)007:7: sku gsum ngo bo gcig tu 'dus phyag 'tshal //
NK033(gi)007:8: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK033(gi)007:9: 'dir rdzogs pa chen po rgyud bcu bdun gyi dbang bskur ba'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK033(gi)007:10: cho ga la 'jug pa gang zag gi mtshan nyid /
NK033(gi)007:11: sngon 'gro legs par bshams pa dang /
NK033(gi)007:13: de la ston byed slob dpon ni mtshan nyid gsum dang ldan dgos te /
NK033(gi)007:14: mdo rgyud kyi don la mkhas pa /
NK033(gi)007:15: mngon sum gyi gnad bsgom pa /
NK033(gi)007:16: rang smin nas gzhan rgyud dgrol nus pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:18: mngon sum snying po'i don ston pa'i bla ma la sangs rgyas dngos kyi 'du shes skye ba /
NK033(gi)007:19: dad pa'i zhing sa bzang ba /
NK033(gi)007:20: mi dge ba dug ltar spong ba /
NK033(gi)007:21: 'khrul pa'i don rig pas yang dag pa'i gdams pa
NK033(gi)007:22: zhu ba la 'jig rten gyi nor rdzas la gtong
NK033(gi)007:23: phod che ba / lus dang srog la mi 'phongs
NK033(gi)007:24: par chos phyir lus srog gtong nus shing sri zhu
NK033(gi)007:26: gnyis pa rdzas bsham pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:27: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi tshad ldan me long gi ngos ltar snyoms pa la /
NK033(gi)007:28: ba byung lnga dang dris byugs pa'i steng du thig tshon ye shes lnga byin gyis brlabs la /
NK033(gi)007:29: tshangs zur nas sgo rkyang gi thig rdzogs par gdab cing /
NK033(gi)007:30: dbus zlum po mthing ga pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK033(gi)007:35: mtshams bzhir mdzes tshon du spel zhing //
NK033(gi)007:38: zhing khams dang bcas pa'i mthar nyi zla pad+ma rdo
NK033(gi)007:39: rje'i ra ba 'od zer lnga'i phreng bas bskor bar
NK033(gi)007:40: bris pa'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir rin po che'i bum
NK033(gi)007:41: pa rigs lnga'i kha dog can so so'i sa bon
NK033(gi)007:42: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aas mtshan pa kha brgyan mgul chings dang
NK033(gi)007:43: bcas pa bkod / bum pa'i nang du rin po che lnga /
NK033(gi)007:47: snying po lnga rnams gangs kyi chu gtsang 'o ma dang sbyar ba dkar gsum /
NK033(gi)007:48: mngar gsum gyis bran pas bkang zhing /
NK033(gi)007:49: kha rgyan gyi gseb tu me long lnga /
NK033(gi)007:53: rigs lnga'i tsaka li dang bcas pa bkod /
NK033(gi)007:54: gsang dbang gi rdzas thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba kha me long gis bcad /
NK033(gi)007:55: sin+d+hu ras byugs pa'i kha dar dmar pos bkab la bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:56: sgo bzhir phur pa bzhi dang /
NK033(gi)007:59: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa sman raka gtor gsum dang /
NK033(gi)007:60: tshogs kyi 'khor lo rgya cher bsham /
NK033(gi)007:61: bla bre dang yol ba la sogs bkod pas brgyan pa dang /
NK033(gi)007:62: byang shar du pad+ma 'dab bzhi dbus ljang gu'i steng
NK033(gi)007:63: du las kyi bum pa dri bzang gi chus bkang
NK033(gi)007:64: zhing / kha rgyan mgul chings sogs bkod pas brgyan pa bsham par bya'o //
NK033(gi)007:65: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la /
NK033(gi)007:66: bdag dang dkyil 'khor byin gyis brlab pa /
NK033(gi)007:69: de yang gsang sngags phyi pa ltar bskyed rdzogs du
NK033(gi)007:70: ma'i spros pa med na'ang ye nas dkyil 'khor sangs
NK033(gi)007:72: gnas skabs su gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK033(gi)007:73: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bsdus pa zhig byas la /
NK033(gi)007:74: rang nyid skad cig gis gzhi'i kun tu bzang po yab yum mthing ga mnyam sbyor /
NK033(gi)007:75: phyag gnyis mnyam bzhag zhabs skyil krung //
NK033(gi)007:76: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa 'od zer du ma 'phro bar bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:78: mdun du rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor skad cig gis bskyed la /
NK033(gi)007:80: snang srid snod bcud thams cad rigs lnga'i zhing khams
NK033(gi)007:81: gzhal yas khang lha dang lha mos gang ba 'dod
NK033(gi)007:84: las bum du rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa bskyed /
NK033(gi)007:86: de nas slob mas man+dala phul ba'i rjes su thal mo sbyar la /
NK033(gi)007:87: e ma hoh skyes mchog 'gro mgon bla ma rje //
NK033(gi)007:88: bdag ni las can rigs kyi bu //
NK033(gi)007:89: gsang chen nges pa'i lung 'di la //
NK033(gi)007:90: rtogs pas bdag nyid bzung du gsol //
NK033(gi)007:92: de nas bla mas gnang ba byin pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:93: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK033(gi)007:94: shin tu gsang ba'i theg pa 'dir //
NK033(gi)007:95: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gi lung //
NK033(gi)007:97: bdag nyid chen po khyed cag ni //
NK033(gi)007:98: blo yi the tshom rab bsal nas //
NK033(gi)007:99: nor bu'i yon tan mthong ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)007:100: bdag cag bla mar spro lags sam //
NK033(gi)007:102: slob bus spro lags zhes zhu /
NK033(gi)007:103: de nas skyabs 'gro bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:106: rlung lnga rnam par dag pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:107: nyon mongs rnam dag ye shes lnga //
NK033(gi)007:108: sku gsum mdzad pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:109: dkon mchog gsum la rtogs pas 'dud //
NK033(gi)007:111: de nas bla mas 'di skad brjod /
NK033(gi)007:112: skal ldan rang gi lus kyi 'khor lo bzhi dam chos //
NK033(gi)007:114: thig le lnga'i dwangs ma ye shes ni nyon mongs
NK033(gi)007:115: pa ye nas dag pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi
NK033(gi)007:116: bdag nyid du ngo shes nas bsgom snyam du don
NK033(gi)007:117: dam pa'i skyabs su 'gro ba gyis shig /
NK033(gi)007:119: de nas smon pa sems bskyed ni /
NK033(gi)007:120: e ma hoh ma rig 'jig rten mun pa'i klong //
NK033(gi)007:121: rang gi thabs shes sgron me yis //
NK033(gi)007:122: rang la gnas pa'i ye shes de //
NK033(gi)007:123: bla ma'i drin gyis rtogs par bya //
NK033(gi)007:125: de nas rang rig mngon sum gyi ye shes snang
NK033(gi)007:126: ba bzhi nyams su blang snyam du sems bla na
NK033(gi)007:130: e ma hoh sangs rgyas mthar thug dbyings rig gnyis //
NK033(gi)007:131: sku gsum ngo bo mtha' bral gzhi //
NK033(gi)007:132: tshig las 'das pa'i rang byung de //
NK033(gi)007:133: da lta nyid du rtogs bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:135: de ni dbyings ka dag chos sku nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK033(gi)007:136: ye shes lhun grub rang rig chos sku sku gsum
NK033(gi)007:137: gyi ngo bo spros pa'i mtha' bzhi las 'das pa
NK033(gi)007:138: / de nyid tshig dang yi ge med pa'i don
NK033(gi)007:139: smra bsam brjod med chen po nyid rang ngo shes
NK033(gi)007:140: par bya snyam du sems bskyed cig /
NK033(gi)007:142: de nas srung skud gdags pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:143: tshon sna lnga'i skud pa la /
NK033(gi)007:144: +aahh+aum swa b+h+aa ba bi shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa ba bi shud+d+ho &aham /
NK033(gi)007:145: zhes pa'i sngags kyis mdud pa byas la /
NK033(gi)007:147: mo'i dpung pa g.yon la gdags so //
NK033(gi)007:148: de nas dam bsgrag pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:149: las bum gyi chu phor du blugs la /
NK033(gi)007:151: 'di ni dam tshig rdo rje'i chu //
NK033(gi)007:152: nyams na dmyal me bzod dkas bsreg /
NK033(gi)007:153: bskal pa grangs med sdug bsngal 'gyur //
NK033(gi)007:154: bsrung na dngos grub rmad po che //
NK033(gi)007:155: ma lus lhun gyis grub par 'gyur //
NK033(gi)007:156: de bas dam tshig srog gi chu //
NK033(gi)007:157: snying la zhog la thub par gyis //
NK033(gi)007:160: dam tshig nyams na dmyal ba las thar pa'i dus med cing /
NK033(gi)007:161: sdug bsngal bzod blag med pa myong dgos pas /
NK033(gi)007:164: zhes rdo rje spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:165: de nas slob ma'i rgyud dag pa'i phyir /
NK033(gi)007:166: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i khrus kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:167: las bum gyis slob ma bsangs la /
NK033(gi)007:169: h+aum las rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa sku mdog
NK033(gi)007:170: ljang sngon zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa spyan gsum dang
NK033(gi)007:171: ldan pa / zhabs rdo rje skyil krung /
NK033(gi)007:172: phyag g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje dang g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK033(gi)007:173: rgyud rang nas rnam 'joms sngon po //
NK033(gi)007:174: g.yas bum pa dkar po rdo rje rgya gram gyis kha bcad pa /
NK033(gi)007:175: g.yon sdigs mdzub phur pa 'dril ba /
NK033(gi)007:176: klu rigs bzhis sku la brgyan pa gcig gsungs 'dug /
NK033(gi)007:177: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i sku
NK033(gi)007:178: gsung thugs kyi yi ge gsum las 'od zer 'phros
NK033(gi)007:179: bas / rang bzhin gyi gnas dang byang shar lcang
NK033(gi)007:180: lo can gyi gnas nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje
NK033(gi)007:181: rnam par 'joms pa la sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK033(gi)007:182: sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba spyan drangs /
NK033(gi)007:183: gnyis su med par thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:184: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug cing rol mo'i sgra bsgrag la /
NK033(gi)007:185: na mahtsan+da badz+ra kro d+ha ya hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)007:186: sngags 'di nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas la /
NK033(gi)007:187: spyi bor rdo rje rgya gram bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:189: las kyi bum pa de nyid /
NK033(gi)007:190: b+h+r+aum las bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa /
NK033(gi)007:191: phyi bum pa'i rnam pa la nang bcud gzhal yas
NK033(gi)007:192: khang du bsams pa'i pad zla'i steng du rdo rje
NK033(gi)007:193: rnam 'joms la khrus kyi lha mos bskor bar bsam
NK033(gi)007:194: la / ye shes pa dgug cing bstim /
NK033(gi)007:196: lcang lo can gyi pho brang dam pa sogs bstod pa ci rigs pas bstod /
NK033(gi)007:197: lha tshogs 'od dang ldan pas bdud rtsi'i bum pa de nyid bdud rtsis gang bar bsam /
NK033(gi)007:199: badz+ra tsan+da sarba a bud+d+ha ram /
NK033(gi)007:200: yam sarba bud+d+ha ho ram ram bam ram ram badz+ra tsan+da ram ram /
NK033(gi)007:202: de nas bum pa spyi bor bzhag la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:204: bdud rtsi dag pa'i ye shes sku //
NK033(gi)007:205: chos nyid mkha' mnyam ye shes bum //
NK033(gi)007:206: rnam dag kun spyod ye shes chu //
NK033(gi)007:207: rig pa'i ye shes snying por bcas //
NK033(gi)007:208: mkha' gsang mnyam sbyor lan tsh+wa'i ro //
NK033(gi)007:209: rnam dag dri med bcud len sman //
NK033(gi)007:210: 'dod yon las grub rin po che //
NK033(gi)007:212: gso byed rdo rje'o ma'i chu //
NK033(gi)007:214: mnyen 'grol thugs rje dar dpyangs dang //
NK033(gi)007:215: 'bras bu bcud kyis gtams pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:216: chos nyid mnyam pa'i bum pa mchog /
NK033(gi)007:217: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:218: chos nyid rang stobs rnyed nas kyang //
NK033(gi)007:219: dbang chen sku dang ldan gyur cig /
NK033(gi)007:220: ma h+aa ka la sha sid+d+hi badz+ra h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:222: de nas khrus kyi bum pas khrus bya zhing /
NK033(gi)007:225: rnam dag dri med ye shes chu //
NK033(gi)007:226: bkrus pas rnam rtog dri ma kun sbyong zhing //
NK033(gi)007:227: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams kyi //
NK033(gi)007:228: ye shes chu rgyun babs nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:229: khyod kyi rnam rtog byang gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:230: phyi dang nang gi sdug bsngal rnams //
NK033(gi)007:231: thams cad zhi bar gyur nas kyang //
NK033(gi)007:232: ye shes snang ba gsal bar ston //
NK033(gi)007:233: dag pa ye shes bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:234: dri ma'i skyon rnams byang ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:235: mi gtsang la sogs nyams pa kun //
NK033(gi)007:236: shel gong lta bur gyur nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:237: rnam 'joms nyid kyi sku gsung thugs //
NK033(gi)007:238: rigs kyi bu la snang bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:239: badz+ra tsan+da kro d+ha k+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)007:240: de nas gtor ma spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:241: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa kro d+ha hu lu hu lu /
NK033(gi)007:242: b+han d+ha b+han d+ha hu lu hu lu h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:243: ba ling ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:244: rdo rje rnam 'joms khrus dbang ngo //
NK033(gi)007:245: de nas dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing bkra shis brjod par bya'o ////
NK033(gi)007:246: de nas dngos gzhi'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:247: slob ma rnams gdong dar dmar pos dkris la /
NK033(gi)007:248: lag tu me tog bzung la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:250: rdo rje slob dpon gnyan gyis dbu bzung nas //
NK033(gi)007:251: yi dam lha dang mkha' 'gro dam tshig can //
NK033(gi)007:252: thams cad ma lus bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK033(gi)007:253: dkyil 'khor 'dir 'jug bdag la dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:254: gsang ba chen pos bdag la gnang bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:256: slar dam tshig bskyar zhing nan tan du bya ba ni dam chu blud la /
NK033(gi)007:257: dam tshig khro chu khol ma 'di //
NK033(gi)007:258: khyod la gtad kyi thub par gyis //
NK033(gi)007:259: nyams na dmyal ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK033(gi)007:260: thub na yon tan rtsa brgyad thob //
NK033(gi)007:261: de bas khyod kyis gus pas longs //
NK033(gi)007:263: bag sha ni ho hoh de nas ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:264: slob ma kun bzang yab yum du bskyed la /
NK033(gi)007:265: rtsa gnas 'khor lo bzhi yi rtsa dang yi ge dang thig le sku dang 'od zer 'phro ba /
NK033(gi)007:266: snying nang dang dung khang du zhi khro'i lha tshogs gsal gdab la /
NK033(gi)007:267: slob dpon gyis d+aa dril dkrol zhing /
NK033(gi)007:268: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK033(gi)007:269: lte ba sprul sku'i bzhugs gnas yin //
NK033(gi)007:270: rlung lnga g.yo rtsol las 'das pas //
NK033(gi)007:271: thig le 'od skur shigs se shig /
NK033(gi)007:272: snying ga chos sku'i bzhugs gnas su //
NK033(gi)007:273: sangs rgya rigs lnga yab yum bzhugs //
NK033(gi)007:274: 'od zer lnga ru shigs se shig /
NK033(gi)007:275: mgrin pa longs spyod pho brang du //
NK033(gi)007:276: sems dpa' rgyal ba rgya mtsho bzhugs //
NK033(gi)007:277: thig le 'od skur ya la la //
NK033(gi)007:278: spyi bor bde chen 'khor lo na //
NK033(gi)007:280: khro rgyal gad rgyangs ya la la //
NK033(gi)007:281: bo d+hi tsit+ta sh+aan+tim kro d+ha sa pa ri w+aa ra a be sha ya a a /
NK033(gi)007:282: zhes rol mo'i sgras byin phab /
NK033(gi)007:283: gu gul sha chen sogs kyi dud pas bdug /
NK033(gi)007:284: rdo rje spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:285: su pra tish+thasa brtan par byas /
NK033(gi)007:286: de nas me tog dor ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:287: e ma hoh thog ma med pa'i dus dag nas //
NK033(gi)007:288: da lta'i dus 'di yan chod du //
NK033(gi)007:289: sngon nas las 'brel yod pa'i lha //
NK033(gi)007:290: rigs mchog de la 'bab par shog /
NK033(gi)007:292: me tog dal gyi dbus su bab na /
NK033(gi)007:294: shar du rdo rje snying po /
NK033(gi)007:296: nub tu bde chen rgyal po /
NK033(gi)007:297: byang du sgo lnga bya bral zhes btags so //
NK033(gi)007:298: de nas mig dbye ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:299: e ma skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK033(gi)007:300: khyod kyi ma rig rmongs pa'i mig /
NK033(gi)007:301: ye shes spyan du ngas phye'o //
NK033(gi)007:305: mig zim bus dkyil 'khor gyi nang du bltas la /
NK033(gi)007:306: mdog dkar ser dmar ljang mthing sogs /
NK033(gi)007:307: rigs so so'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)007:308: de nas gser gyi thur mas dkyil 'khor bstan la /
NK033(gi)007:309: de yang dbus zlum po mthing gar byung ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:310: gzhi chos nyid kyi don la gnyen po dang bral ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:311: pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon du byung ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:312: gzhi la rlung lnga'i dwangs ma dang ldan pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:313: gru chad bzhir byung ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:315: khyams bzhi sgo dang bcas pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:316: phrin las bzhi po rang la tshang ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:317: pany+tsa re kh+aa'i rtsig pa lngar byung ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:318: ye shes lnga'i ra ba dang ldan pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:320: gzhi la tshad med bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:322: rtag pa brtan pa 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis
NK033(gi)007:323: grub pa'i gzhi'i dbyings gdod ma nas gnas pa'i barda'o
NK033(gi)007:325: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang na gnas pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:327: 'dod yon ma spang rgyan du shar ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:329: 'dod yon ma spangs rang las byung ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:331: gzhi'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:333: thugs rje la phyogs ris med pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:335: 'od gsal snying por gyur pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:337: rang snang lhun gyis grub pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:339: shes rab dbyings su 'khyil ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:341: ye shes dri mas ma gos pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:344: 'od zer gyi phreng bas bskor ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:345: dbyings na sku dang ye shes lnga'i rol pa lhun gyis grub pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:347: de nas rdzas kyi mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:348: e ma brda shes skal ldan bu //
NK033(gi)007:349: brda dang dam rdzas bkod pa'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)007:350: gnas lugs mtshon pa'i rdzas 'di ltos //
NK033(gi)007:351: mthong ba'i don ni bdag la smos //
NK033(gi)007:354: thams cad chos nyid kyi rol par mthong lags /
NK033(gi)007:356: bla mas rdzas kyi de nyid bstan pa ni //
NK033(gi)007:359: bum pa lngar byung ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:360: rigs lnga rang la rdzogs pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:362: yum lnga yab lnga dbyer med pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:364: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ye nas rdzogs pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:366: ngo bo ka dag chos sku'i gzhi mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:368: rang bzhin 'od mdangs sgron ma lnga rang la 'char bas lhun grub longs sku'i zhing mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:370: thugs rje'i rig pa'i snying po ye shes lnga ldan
NK033(gi)007:371: sprul pa 'phro ba'i gzhi mtshon pa'i mda' lnga ni
NK033(gi)007:372: / shes rab gzhi la mtshon pa'i dar sna lnga ni /
NK033(gi)007:373: rlung lnga dbyings na mtshon pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:375: rig pa chos dbyings 'pho 'gyur med pa mtha' bzhi las grol ba'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:377: rig pa'i ngo bor rtogs pas skyes bzhi'i mngal sgo chod pa'i barda'o //
NK033(gi)007:378: phyi nang gi mchod pa gtor tshogs gnas kyi bkod pa phun sum tshogs pas brgyan pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:379: snang srid snod bcud kyi 'jig rten 'dod yon sgo
NK033(gi)007:380: lnga'i snang yul thams cad rang rig pa'i ngang nas
NK033(gi)007:381: rmi lam sgyu ma ltar 'gags pa med pa ye
NK033(gi)007:384: de nas bla mas mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:385: skal ldan gyi slob bu khyod kyis bla ma cir mthong /
NK033(gi)007:387: bla ma khyod nyid sangs rgyas kyi lam ston pa'i gnas su mthong lags /
NK033(gi)007:388: de nas mched lcam mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:389: e ma ngo mtshar rigs kyi bu //
NK033(gi)007:390: grogs kyi dam pa gang yin pa //
NK033(gi)007:391: 'jug sgo gcig pa'i mched lcam la //
NK033(gi)007:392: dag pa'i snang ba mthong ring na //
NK033(gi)007:393: khyod kyi mthong ba bdag la smros //
NK033(gi)007:395: thar pa bsgrub pa'i grogs rnams lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du mthong lags /
NK033(gi)007:397: de nas dbang bskur bar gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:398: e ma rin chen bla ma dang //
NK033(gi)007:399: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs kyis //
NK033(gi)007:400: bdag cag skal ldan bu dag la //
NK033(gi)007:401: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog rnams //
NK033(gi)007:402: dus 'dir bdag la gnang bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:404: slob dpon gyis rdo rje dril bu slob ma'i lag tu gtad la /
NK033(gi)007:406: chos nyid dbyings kyi rdo rje dang //
NK033(gi)007:407: shes rab rang bzhin dril bu zungs //
NK033(gi)007:408: sgra yis thams cad zil gyis mnan //
NK033(gi)007:409: dril bu dkrol zhing rdo rje gsor //
NK033(gi)007:410: thabs shes zung 'jug dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:411: badz+ra tsit+ta gan+de a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:412: de nas dbus kyi bum pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:414: chos nyid stong pa ye shes dag pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:415: rnam dag don ldan ye shes bum pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:416: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:417: stong rig gsal ba'i don ldan shog /
NK033(gi)007:418: badz+ra tsit+ta ye ti ta badz+ra a ni s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)007:419: lho'i bum pa rna ltag gnyis su bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:421: stong nyid ye shes las byung ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:422: chos sku dag pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK033(gi)007:423: ye shes dag pa'i pho brang 'dir //
NK033(gi)007:424: bkra shis dag pa'i bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:425: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:426: rat+na e bam ti ta dza h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:427: nub bum mgrin par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:429: rtog pa'i dra ba sel ba'i bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:430: dag pa'i ye shes gnyis dang sbyor //
NK033(gi)007:431: ye shes ston pa'i bum pa rab mdzes pas //
NK033(gi)007:432: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:433: pad+ma du di sha ri hi bag s+t+wam /
NK033(gi)007:434: byang gi bum pa lte ba dang yan lag bzhi la bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:436: byang chub las byung bdud rtsi'i snod //
NK033(gi)007:437: nyon mongs sel ba'i bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:438: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:439: karma dz+ny+aa na tam bag sham h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:440: dbang rdzas kyi mda' bzhi spyi bo dang lag par gtad la /
NK033(gi)007:442: ye shes gsal ba'i sgo bzhir ldan //
NK033(gi)007:443: shes rab skyed pa'i mda' bzhi yis //
NK033(gi)007:444: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:445: snang ba bzhi dang 'phrad par shog /
NK033(gi)007:446: dzahh+aum bam hoh kha ga dzahya /
NK033(gi)007:447: ral gri bzhi lag par gtad la /
NK033(gi)007:449: shes rab don ldan ral gri bzhis //
NK033(gi)007:450: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:451: mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:452: badz+ra pradz+ny+aa ma h+aa bag sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:453: me long bzhi snying gar bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:455: chos nyid rnam dag stong pa'i rgyu //
NK033(gi)007:457: thams cad de yi don la gnas //
NK033(gi)007:458: chos nyid ye shes mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK033(gi)007:459: me long 'di la brten pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:460: skal ldan 'di chos dbyings ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:461: d+harma d+h+aa tu dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sarba +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)007:462: me long bzhi snying gar bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:464: nyon mongs dag pa'i ye shes rgyu //
NK033(gi)007:465: gsal 'grib med pa'i don rtogs pa //
NK033(gi)007:466: rdzas kyi me long dam pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:467: skal ldan me long ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:468: a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra sarba +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)007:469: me long bzhi snying gar bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:471: yab yum gnyis med dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK033(gi)007:472: ye shes stong gsal mnyam pa'i me long 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:473: skal ldan mnyam nyid ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:474: rat+na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)007:475: me long bzhi snying gar bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:477: thams cad 'byung ba'i ye shes dag pa'i rdzas //
NK033(gi)007:478: deng gi skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:479: sor rtog ye shes dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:480: pad+ma a ti badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)007:481: me long bzhi snying gar bzhag h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:482: thams cad gnyis med gcig tu bsdus pa'i ye shes de //
NK033(gi)007:483: chos rnams bya ba rdzogs par ston mdzad pas //
NK033(gi)007:484: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:485: bya grub ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:486: karma dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK033(gi)007:487: rma bya'i sgro chun gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:489: kha dog thams cad ston mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:490: lhun grub dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK033(gi)007:491: mu khyud ra bar ston mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:493: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:494: rin chen spubs su sangs rgyas shog /
NK033(gi)007:495: pra be sha ya 'du sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:496: gtor ma spyi bo dang lag par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:498: sna tshogs pa yi rdzas chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:499: 'di dang phyi ma gnyis ka ru //
NK033(gi)007:501: byin rlabs drag po'i gtor ma 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:502: skal ldan bar chad thams cad bsal ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:503: sangs rgyas byin rlabs gnang bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:504: ba lid+ta du sha ya na h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:505: mig la thig le byas la dkyil 'khor bltar bcug la /
NK033(gi)007:507: rnam dag dri med chos kyi spyan //
NK033(gi)007:508: do nub khyod la mngon gyur shog /
NK033(gi)007:509: spyi dang rang gi don shes pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:510: gang yang ma 'gags shes rab spyan //
NK033(gi)007:511: do nub khyod la gsal bar gyis //
NK033(gi)007:513: phyi dang nang med kun gsal ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:514: rang bzhin ma g.yos rig pa'i spyan //
NK033(gi)007:515: do nub khyod la gsal gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:516: rig pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar ltos //
NK033(gi)007:518: dngos dang dngos med snang ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:519: bdag gzhan thams cad don gsal ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:520: thams cad mkhyen nyid bzhi yi spyan //
NK033(gi)007:521: do nub khyod la gsal gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:522: rig pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar ltos //
NK033(gi)007:524: thogs pa med pa'i spyan mnga' yis //
NK033(gi)007:525: dkyil 'khor phyogs mtshams kun nas ltos //
NK033(gi)007:526: gnas bzhir dri'i thig le byas te dkyil 'khor sgo bzhir bltar bcug la /
NK033(gi)007:528: shar gyi sgo na rig pa gsal //
NK033(gi)007:529: rig pa ye shes mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:530: ye shes dag pa'i snang ba 'char //
NK033(gi)007:531: de phyir shar gyi sgo zhes bya //
NK033(gi)007:532: de yang khyod la bstan pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:533: ma bred ma dngangs myur du ltos //
NK033(gi)007:534: chags med spyan gyis bltas pa na //
NK033(gi)007:535: 'gyur med ye shes dag pa mthong //
NK033(gi)007:537: lho sgo ye shes bskyed pa'i rtags //
NK033(gi)007:538: snang ba lhug par 'char ba'i brda //
NK033(gi)007:539: ye shes mig gis ma chags ltos //
NK033(gi)007:541: nub sgo bag chags nub pa'i sgo //
NK033(gi)007:542: dug lnga ye shes lnga ldan 'od //
NK033(gi)007:544: shes rab mig gis bltas byas nas //
NK033(gi)007:545: khyod kyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs mthong //
NK033(gi)007:547: byang sgo sa lam sbyong ba'i sgo //
NK033(gi)007:548: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i sgo //
NK033(gi)007:549: las rab rdzogs pa'i sgo chen 'di //
NK033(gi)007:550: mkhyen gsal mig gis myur du ltos //
NK033(gi)007:551: rdo rje rang rtags chen po 'di //
NK033(gi)007:552: sems can kun gyi rang rgyud la //
NK033(gi)007:553: dkyil 'khor de bzhin gnas pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:554: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor de bzhin du //
NK033(gi)007:555: rang gi lus la yod pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:556: de bzhin dkyil 'khor pho brang ltos //
NK033(gi)007:557: rang lus gzhal yas khang gi tshul //
NK033(gi)007:558: lha rnams ma bskyed lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK033(gi)007:559: de phyir dbang gi dkyil 'khor ltos //
NK033(gi)007:560: myur du bltas na dngos grub thob //
NK033(gi)007:561: sarba ta th+aa ga ta man+da la a s+t+wam h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:565: bo d+hi sat+wa mu na ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:566: a li ka li dang ye d+har+m+aa brjod la /
NK033(gi)007:568: tshogs kyi 'khor lo la rol par bya'o //
NK033(gi)007:569: de lta bu'i dbang gi dngos grub thob pa la /
NK033(gi)007:570: phyi dbang rdzogs nas longs spyod thams cad 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)007:571: chos nyid rtags mthong phung po ye shes lngar rdzogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:572: de yan zhi ba byang chub sems su dbang bskur ba'o ////
NK033(gi)007:573: da ni khro bo'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:577: de'i phyi rim mu khyud zlum po /
NK033(gi)007:584: rdo rje'i ra ba sgo rgyan sogs mdzes par bris pa'i dbus su bkod pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:585: dbus kyi 'khor lo'i gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)007:586: skyes pa bud med ban+d+ha pho thod la yi ge brum /
NK033(gi)007:587: mo thod la ma bris la /
NK033(gi)007:588: de'i mdun du bud med phru gu ma skyes pa'i tshil bu /
NK033(gi)007:590: thod pa gcig gi nang du sha khrag sna tshogs kyi gtor ma bsham /
NK033(gi)007:591: zla gam gsum gyi steng du /
NK033(gi)007:592: bum pa'i nang du rin po che dang sman sna tshogs /
NK033(gi)007:593: bum pa'i kha dog dmar po bya /
NK033(gi)007:594: dar dmar gyi mgul chings byas pa rnams bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:597: gru chad re re la me long re dang /
NK033(gi)007:599: zla gam steng du b+han+b+ha gling bzhi mtshan ldan du /
NK033(gi)007:600: gtor ma bdud rtsis bran pa dar mthing gas kha bcad /
NK033(gi)007:601: lho phyogs su tshil chen gyi mar me /
NK033(gi)007:602: nub tu seng ldeng gi phur pa dar gyis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)007:603: dpral bar thal chen gyis mtshan ma bris /
NK033(gi)007:605: snying la zhag gi zo ris /
NK033(gi)007:606: mgo la dbang zhus legs par brgyan la /
NK033(gi)007:608: dur khrod chas kyis mtshan ma btab la /
NK033(gi)007:611: khro rgyal yab dang yum dang bcas //
NK033(gi)007:612: thams cad gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK033(gi)007:613: bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad kun //
NK033(gi)007:614: khro bo'i mtshan thos tsam gyis kyang //
NK033(gi)007:616: sdug bsngal chen pos zin pas na //
NK033(gi)007:618: hoh dgongs shig rol cig khro rgyal rnams //
NK033(gi)007:619: slob ma 'jug cing gnang bar mdzad du gsol //
NK033(gi)007:620: dug gsum rtsad gcod 'khor ba'i dbyings nas thon //
NK033(gi)007:621: nga ni khro rgyal pad+ma ste //
NK033(gi)007:622: nga ni dkyil 'khor rdzas ston gyis //
NK033(gi)007:623: 'byung po'i tshogs rnams rab tu dengs //
NK033(gi)007:624: khyod la dbang gi skal ba med //
NK033(gi)007:625: dbang mchog thob par mi 'gyur gyi //
NK033(gi)007:626: phyi ma'i dus kyi tha ma la //
NK033(gi)007:627: ston pa rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK033(gi)007:628: khyod la dbang gi brda ston gyi //
NK033(gi)007:629: 'di la skal med phyir dengs shig /
NK033(gi)007:630: hoh dbang gi skal ba mi ldan pa rnams //
NK033(gi)007:631: dbang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir yang sa tshon gyi dkyil
NK033(gi)007:632: 'khor 'jig pa dang bcas par mthong ba yin no
NK033(gi)007:633: // rdzas rnams mang po dbang po rtul ba dang mi ldan pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:634: gsang ba dbang gi dkyil 'khor 'di la yid ma ches pa dang /
NK033(gi)007:635: de lta bu'i 'du shes dang ldan pa rnams la /
NK033(gi)007:636: dbang ra na po che 'di'i skal ba med pas
NK033(gi)007:637: dbang bskur kyang bskal bar nus pa mi 'byung bas
NK033(gi)007:638: / rigs kyi bu rnams de ltar ma byed cig /
NK033(gi)007:640: de nas slob ma skad cig gis /
NK033(gi)007:641: pad+ma he ru kar bskyed pa gong 'og tu yang
NK033(gi)007:642: mang du gsungs kyang rdzogs pa rang byung gi rgyud
NK033(gi)007:643: las / pad+ma he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK033(gi)007:644: g.yas ljang g.yon sngo dbus dmar //
NK033(gi)007:645: phyag drug g.yas gsum dgra s+t+wa mdung thung ral gri /
NK033(gi)007:646: g.yon gsum bam dbyug thod pa sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
NK033(gi)007:647: dbu yi steng rta mgo gsum gyis rta skad 'tsher
NK033(gi)007:648: ba me dpung gi klong du bzhugs pa bskyed par
NK033(gi)007:649: gsungs so // pad+ma he ru kar gsal ba'i thod pa dung khang du /
NK033(gi)007:650: 'bar ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du gsal btab la /
NK033(gi)007:651: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku gsung thugs las 'od 'phros /
NK033(gi)007:652: steng phyogs me ri 'bar ba'i pho brang nas /
NK033(gi)007:653: khro bo'i lha tshogs slob ma'i lus la rgya mtsho la char pa bzhin thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:654: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri sa
NK033(gi)007:655: pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra a be sha ya a
NK033(gi)007:657: tshil chen gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK033(gi)007:658: spyi bor rdo rje bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:659: tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas //
NK033(gi)007:660: de nas zhun chen gyi mar me slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:661: zangs zhu zla gam gzugs can bkon la /
NK033(gi)007:663: thugs rje'i 'od dang ldan par gyur pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:664: snang srid thams cad ye shes lnga yi 'od //
NK033(gi)007:665: 'byung ba lnga lnga ye shes lnga yis khyab //
NK033(gi)007:666: ye shes lnga las byung ba'i 'od lnga 'di //
NK033(gi)007:667: gnyis med chen por gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)007:668: yab lnga'i dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:670: sems can 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:671: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams su //
NK033(gi)007:672: rgyal ba yab dang gnas par shog /
NK033(gi)007:673: nu ti sha ti sha ni h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:674: tshil chen gu gul dud pas bdug la /
NK033(gi)007:676: ye shes lnga dang 'od lnga dang //
NK033(gi)007:677: yab lnga dang ni yum lnga yis //
NK033(gi)007:678: dbang bskur dbang sa non pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:679: ye shes rang lus dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK033(gi)007:680: rdo rje sa med brjid pa'i 'od //
NK033(gi)007:681: dbang gi ye shes 'od mchog dam pa 'di //
NK033(gi)007:682: rang gi tsit+ta'i dkyil na gnas pa'i 'od //
NK033(gi)007:683: ngas bstan khyod kyis nges par longs //
NK033(gi)007:684: 'di bstan pa yi yon tan gyis //
NK033(gi)007:685: rang gi dag pa mthong bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:686: ma h+aa sa la sha s+t+wam bag sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:689: 'byung chen sna lnga ye shes lnga las byung //
NK033(gi)007:690: rig pa nyid mtshon ye shes lnga yi rdzas //
NK033(gi)007:691: kun kyang mi mnyam ye shes lnga 'od kyis //
NK033(gi)007:692: 'gyur med pho brang bstan gyi nye bar longs //
NK033(gi)007:693: 'byung ba ye shes dag pa'i rdzas 'di ni //
NK033(gi)007:694: sems can khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:695: ye shes chig chod 'bar bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:696: +amo du ka sha ti s+t+wam bag sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:699: 'byung ba dang bcas dbang gi dkyil 'khor te //
NK033(gi)007:700: dri med dbang gi ye shes rol pa ye shes dbang bskur sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam pa'i 'od /
NK033(gi)007:701: 'od lnga nyid las rig pa'i sku lnga gsal //
NK033(gi)007:702: ye shes dus dam ldan pa'i rdzas chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:703: sems can 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:704: ngo bo'i snang ba mthong bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:705: dz+ny+aa na s+t+wam bag sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:708: rdo rje'i rigs dang bud+d+ha'i rigs //
NK033(gi)007:709: rin chen rigs dang pad+ma'i rigs //
NK033(gi)007:710: las kyi rigs la sogs pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:711: sangs rgyas kun gyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK033(gi)007:712: bdag cag yang dag mtha' bral shog /
NK033(gi)007:713: da du sha s+t+wam bag sha h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:716: b+han+d+ha ye shes rnam par dag /
NK033(gi)007:718: rnam pa ye shes gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)007:719: sems can 'di la bskur bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:720: 'di la bskur ba'i yon tan gyis //
NK033(gi)007:721: 'di yi bar chad bsal ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:722: phyi mar gzhal yas khang ldan shog /
NK033(gi)007:724: phur pa gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:726: dgra dang bgegs bzlog phur bu 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:727: gang la btab pa brlag par byed //
NK033(gi)007:728: thal ba bzhin du brlag nas kyang //
NK033(gi)007:729: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK033(gi)007:730: rig pa 'di dang dbyer med tshul //
NK033(gi)007:731: rang la yod pa'i ye shes de //
NK033(gi)007:732: bar chad bsal nas mthong bar gyur //
NK033(gi)007:733: des na phur pa'i dbang bskur longs //
NK033(gi)007:734: brjid ta k+ai li k+ai la ya ka sa pa ni h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:735: thod pa mar me tshil chen gsum gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:737: rgyal ba kun gyis basngagasa pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:738: thod pa mar me tshil chen rnam gsum gyi //
NK033(gi)007:739: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK033(gi)007:740: dbang bskur khyod la rdzogs par shog /
NK033(gi)007:742: gong rdzas gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:744: rig pa dang ni ye shes kyi //
NK033(gi)007:745: snang ba dam pa 'di yin pas //
NK033(gi)007:746: rigs kyi bu khyod myur du ltos //
NK033(gi)007:747: phyi yi dbyings dang rig pa gnyis //
NK033(gi)007:749: rdzas kyi dbyings dang rig pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:750: do nub khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:751: rnam dag dbyings dang ye shes kyi //
NK033(gi)007:752: dbang bskur dam pa thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:753: man shel gnas lngar bzhag la //
NK033(gi)007:754: ye shes rig pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK033(gi)007:755: thugs rje'i stobs kyis khyod la gnang //
NK033(gi)007:757: do nub khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:759: gsang ba dag pa shes rab thabs ltar snang //
NK033(gi)007:760: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis med shes rab thabs //
NK033(gi)007:761: rdo rje'i don nyid rnam par rig par ldan //
NK033(gi)007:762: rtogs pa'i don ldan shes rab dbyings dang ldan //
NK033(gi)007:763: do nub khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:765: thabs 'di kun la bkod pa'i thabs //
NK033(gi)007:766: shes rab kun la khyab pa'i rtags //
NK033(gi)007:767: nga yis thabs bstan khyod kyis longs //
NK033(gi)007:768: gsang sngags rgyal po'i thabs dag ni //
NK033(gi)007:769: do nub khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:771: +aah dbyings dang rig pa gcig gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:772: rigs lnga rgyal ba yab yum bcu //
NK033(gi)007:773: dbang bskur rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK033(gi)007:774: dbang ni rang rang tsit+ta'i dkyil //
NK033(gi)007:775: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor bstan gyis phyag 'tshol zhig /
NK033(gi)007:777: +aah yang dag bde ba'i sa la mi 'gyur 'khor lo bskor //
NK033(gi)007:778: de yang khyod kyi rang rtags te //
NK033(gi)007:779: do nub nga yis bstan par bya //
NK033(gi)007:781: mchod rten gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:782: theg pa dgu dang ye shes dgu //
NK033(gi)007:783: sa dgu lam dgu ston pa'i rgyud //
NK033(gi)007:784: mi 'jigs pa las thar pa'i ye shes te //
NK033(gi)007:785: 'gro ba mthun byed sprul pa'i sku thob ste //
NK033(gi)007:786: kun gyi mtshon byed mchod rten dam pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:787: do nub khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:788: sprul pa sku yi sa thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:791: sprul pa'i sku las thugs rje 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:792: sprul skur gyur nas 'gro don 'byung ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:793: ye shes thabs kyis pha rol sgrol gyur cig /
NK033(gi)007:794: badz+ra ma h+aa tsan+da sha ya na ne h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:797: ye shes bskyed pa'i shes rab me chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:798: 'gro ba ma rig sel ba'i sgron mar gsal //
NK033(gi)007:799: skye med dbyings su sgrol byed me chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:800: do nub khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:801: skye med ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:802: ag+ni ha la sha +aah rin po che gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:804: rig pa'i ye shes dgos 'dod skong mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:805: ye shes 'gags med shes rab don ston cing //
NK033(gi)007:806: sna tshogs ci yang ston pa'i rig pa'i dbang //
NK033(gi)007:807: dgos 'dod skong mdzad rin chen dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:808: rig pa'i ngo bo nyid dang ldan gyur cig /
NK033(gi)007:812: dri med skyon bral ye shes dag pa'i rdzas //
NK033(gi)007:813: rig pa chags med sems las rnam grol te //
NK033(gi)007:814: rnam par mi rtog rig pa chos kyi sku //
NK033(gi)007:815: dri med skyon bral pad+ma'i sdong po 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:816: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:818: ral gri gnas lnga dang lag tu gtad la /
NK033(gi)007:820: shes rab dang ni gnyis med sbyor bar mdzad //
NK033(gi)007:821: dkyil 'khor nyid dang ye shes sgyu mar rol //
NK033(gi)007:822: gnyis med mtshon pa shes rab ral gri 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:823: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:824: shes rab chen pos rang rgyud grol bar gyis //
NK033(gi)007:825: pra dz+ny+aa k+aa ya sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:827: dkyil 'khor dang ni dbyings kyi ye shes dang //
NK033(gi)007:828: dbyings dang ye shes don sbyor ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:829: phyi yi dbyings dang nang gi ye shes dang //
NK033(gi)007:830: gsang ba'i rig pa chos nyid ngang du 'dus //
NK033(gi)007:831: dbyer med tshul gyis de bzhin gnas pa rnams //
NK033(gi)007:832: nga yis bstan gyis nga la gus pas nyon //
NK033(gi)007:833: ye shes dag pa'i rdzas kyi sprin chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:834: do nub khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:835: dbyings dang ye shes rtogs nas kyang //
NK033(gi)007:836: thugs rje phyogs bcur mdzad par shog /
NK033(gi)007:838: khro bo'i sku gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:840: stong pa nyid ni ye shes sku //
NK033(gi)007:841: sna tshogs 'byung ba rol pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:842: chos sku mtshon pa'i sku mchog 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:843: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:844: mthar phyin 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:846: mchod pa'i lha mo lnga gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:848: skye dang 'chi med rdo rje'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:849: stong nyid rdo rje'i snying po can //
NK033(gi)007:850: dag pa'i ye shes mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:851: dri ma dag pas gzugs skur ston //
NK033(gi)007:852: chos dbyings dag pa'i ye shes mtshon //
NK033(gi)007:853: skye med mchod pa'i sku mchog gis //
NK033(gi)007:854: do nub khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:857: rdo rje 'gyur med rig pa'i dus //
NK033(gi)007:858: rang rtags mtshon pa dbang gi dus //
NK033(gi)007:859: 'gyur med kun rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi //
NK033(gi)007:860: sa lam mthar phyin grol bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:862: rdo rje snying gar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:864: snying po don nyid rnam sbyar phyir //
NK033(gi)007:865: ye shes dag pa'i lam chen dang //
NK033(gi)007:866: snying po rang bcas rdo rje'i don //
NK033(gi)007:867: sangs rgyas gzhi yi snying por bcas //
NK033(gi)007:868: de bzhin kun la gnas pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:869: snying po'i don nyid nga yis bstan //
NK033(gi)007:870: rtogs pa rgyud la skye 'gyur shog /
NK033(gi)007:872: bum pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:874: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dbang bskur ni //
NK033(gi)007:875: bum pa 'di la mdzad pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:876: dbang bskur 'di la byin gyis brlabs //
NK033(gi)007:877: cho 'phrul rgyas par ston pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:878: bum pa 'di la phrin las rdzogs //
NK033(gi)007:879: ye shes dag pa'i dbang bskur 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:880: ma rig 'khor ba rgyun bcad phyir //
NK033(gi)007:881: do nub khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:883: thig le lnga tshon gyi tshom bu spyi bo dang snying gar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:885: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:886: rgyal ba rigs lnga yum lngar gsal //
NK033(gi)007:887: thabs shes rdo rje'i don ldan pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:888: longs spyod rdzogs sku snang bar gsal //
NK033(gi)007:889: rnam dag sangs rgyas mdzad spyod de //
NK033(gi)007:890: da nas brtan pa thob byas te //
NK033(gi)007:891: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:892: ye shes dag pa'i tshom bu 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:893: do nub khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:894: rang snang bar do brtan par shog /
NK033(gi)007:895: badz+ra si ta k+aa ya h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:896: spyi bo dang snying gar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:898: ye shes rang rtags rdo rje'i don nyid brtan //
NK033(gi)007:899: skye 'jigs bral bas sku yi 'od la bzhugs //
NK033(gi)007:900: 'chi dang bral bas gsung gi zer la rol //
NK033(gi)007:901: skye dang 'chi med rdo rje'i don mtshon sku //
NK033(gi)007:902: skye ba med pa'i ye shes a dkar 'di //
NK033(gi)007:903: sems can kun la rtag par yod pa ste //
NK033(gi)007:904: de yi don ni mtshon pa'i 'od lngar gsal //
NK033(gi)007:905: yang dag pa dang dbyer med mnyam pa nyid //
NK033(gi)007:906: don mtshon ye shes rang rtogs mnyam sbyar ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:907: sangs rgyas kun dang dgongs pa mnyam pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:908: rdo rje skye med rang rtags dbang chen 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:909: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:910: skye med ye shes don rtogs sangs rgyas shog /
NK033(gi)007:911: badz+ra ta na k+aa ya ka ra h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:912: bum pa gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:914: chos nyid rtog med ye shes dag pa'i rgyu //
NK033(gi)007:915: gsang sngags las la sbyor ba ste //
NK033(gi)007:916: stong nyid bum pa sman gyis gtams //
NK033(gi)007:917: bdud rtsi dbang rdzogs dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa ste //
NK033(gi)007:918: 'jig rten 'di na med pa 'tshol ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:919: phyi ma ye shes rtogs nas grol gyur cig /
NK033(gi)007:920: bdud rtsi dag pa'i bkra shis bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:921: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:922: rnam dag bdu rtsi ye shes don rtogs shog /
NK033(gi)007:924: bum pa gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:926: stong pa nyid dang ye shes kyi //
NK033(gi)007:927: dbang bskur bdag gis blangs pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:928: rdzas mchog dam pa bdud rtsi'i bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:929: skye med dbyings dang ye shes mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:930: sangs rgyas lam dang ye shes dag pa'i lam //
NK033(gi)007:931: lam sbyangs nas ni ye shes lnga dang sbyar //
NK033(gi)007:932: 'du 'bral med pa'i rig pa rtog med ngang //
NK033(gi)007:933: dbang bskur 'khor lo'i sa la mthar phyin shog /
NK033(gi)007:934: ye shes rtogs pa'i don chen de thob nas //
NK033(gi)007:935: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i sa chen der //
NK033(gi)007:936: sprul pa 'gags med phyogs bcur gsal bar mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:937: de la gnas na sems can don la sbyor //
NK033(gi)007:938: de ltar yon tan kun ldan bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:939: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:940: stong nyid snying po mthar phyin shog /
NK033(gi)007:944: ye shes rgyu mtshan dag pa'i rig pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:945: gsang sngags kun gyi ye shes mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:946: rdzas kyi bum pa stong nyid dag pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:947: gzhon nu bum pa'i sku la mthar phyin pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:948: rang bzhin ma 'gags nyi ma'i 'od ltar gsal //
NK033(gi)007:949: thugs rjes kun nas 'gro ba yongs la khyab //
NK033(gi)007:950: stong gsum ldan pa'i chos nyid dag pa'i don //
NK033(gi)007:951: rang gi de bzhin nyid kyi bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:952: dag pa'i lam mtshan bkra shis bum pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:953: dag pa'i don nyid ye shes spyan sbyar phyir //
NK033(gi)007:954: rgyu mtshan dag pa'i bkra shis bum pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:955: kun gyi don nyid ye shes mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:956: dag pa'i lam dang ye shes gsang lam dang //
NK033(gi)007:957: lam chen 'bras bu dus 'dir mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:958: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:960: thod pa dpral bar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:962: rnam dag ye shes thod pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)007:963: rigs lnga lhun gyi grub pa'i thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:964: gang zag dag pa'i zhing du yam gis bgrod //
NK033(gi)007:965: yi ge yam ldan rdo rje thod pa ste //
NK033(gi)007:966: yi ge de bzhin mkha' la rab bskyod nas //
NK033(gi)007:967: 'gro ba dbyings su 'dren mdzad ye shes thod //
NK033(gi)007:968: dag pa'i don ldan gzhal yas khang gi tshul //
NK033(gi)007:969: rnam dag don spyod rin chen thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:970: dgos 'dod re ba thams cad skong mdzad pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:971: rin chen zur brgyad bkra ba'i thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:972: sems dang ye shes so sor 'byed pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:973: rab tu gsang byed bkra shis thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:974: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:975: gzhal yas khang du yam gis skyod 'gyur shog /
NK033(gi)007:979: skye ba'i ye shes ma yin te //
NK033(gi)007:980: rdzogs pa kun la khyab pa'i don //
NK033(gi)007:981: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyar ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:982: yi ge b+h+r+aum ldan dbyings su 'khyil //
NK033(gi)007:983: b+h+r+aum gyis ma skyod nyid kyi mkha' //
NK033(gi)007:984: ye shes dag pa'i thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:985: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:986: dbyings las phyir mi ldog par shog /
NK033(gi)007:987: badz+ra b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na du ya ni h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:990: shes rab dang ni sku gsung thugs //
NK033(gi)007:991: ngo bo 'gyur med chos kyi don //
NK033(gi)007:992: rang bzhin 'gag med longs sku'i don //
NK033(gi)007:993: thugs rje'i sprul pa phyogs bcur 'phros //
NK033(gi)007:994: sku gsum don ldan yi ge e //
NK033(gi)007:995: sna tshogs e yi gzhal yas khang //
NK033(gi)007:996: e dang ldan pa'i thod pa 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:997: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:998: sku gsum 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:1000: spyi bor byang sems dkar po bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1002: shes rab don byed ye shes ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1003: rang rig sgron ma'i 'od can ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1004: shes rab bskyed pa'i bo d+hi 'dis //
NK033(gi)007:1005: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:1006: shes rab rtogs pa'i don ldan shog /
NK033(gi)007:1008: byang sems dmar po mgrin par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1010: snang srid srid pa'i chos rnams la //
NK033(gi)007:1011: ma rmongs ji ltar shes 'gyur zhing //
NK033(gi)007:1012: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos rnams la //
NK033(gi)007:1013: gang la thogs med shes gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1014: bsod nams ldan zhing sku 'bar dang //
NK033(gi)007:1015: 'gro ba pha rol sgrol bar shog /
NK033(gi)007:1017: mig la dri'i thig le byas te dkyil 'khor bltar bcug la /
NK033(gi)007:1019: shar sgo rdo rje dbyings kyi sgo //
NK033(gi)007:1020: tshom bur blta na 'dir ltos shig /
NK033(gi)007:1021: lho sgo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sgo //
NK033(gi)007:1022: ye shes blta na 'dir ltos shig /
NK033(gi)007:1023: nub sgo sku lnga mthar phyin sgo //
NK033(gi)007:1024: rigs nyid blta na 'dir ltos shig /
NK033(gi)007:1025: byang sgo rdo rje snying po'i sgo //
NK033(gi)007:1026: rigs lnga blta na 'dir ltos shig /
NK033(gi)007:1027: pho brang pad+ma rnam dag sku //
NK033(gi)007:1028: rang lus blta na 'dir ltos shig /
NK033(gi)007:1030: rdo rje spyi bor bzhag cod pan btags /
NK033(gi)007:1032: rang rtags rdo rje don nyid do //
NK033(gi)007:1033: dar dang 'bru yi rang rtags kyi //
NK033(gi)007:1034: 'jig rten 'di yi bar chad bsal ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:1035: rang rtags rdo rje nyid du 'du 'bral med //
NK033(gi)007:1037: 'di la srung zhing skyob pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:1038: dbang rtags 'di ni mthong ba tsam gyis kyang //
NK033(gi)007:1039: bgegs rnams brgyal zhing gzhan du bros //
NK033(gi)007:1040: yams dang rims nad kun las thar ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:1041: dbang rtags 'di yis rab tu bskyabs par gyis //
NK033(gi)007:1042: gnod sbyin rnams dang gsang ba'i rigs rnams dang //
NK033(gi)007:1043: de bzhin mkha' 'gro'i rigs rnams ni //
NK033(gi)007:1044: pad+ma dang ni de bzhin las kyi rigs //
NK033(gi)007:1045: sa dang bar snang gnas pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:1046: ri rab dang ni mtshon la gnas //
NK033(gi)007:1048: 'di la sku yis bsrung bar gyis //
NK033(gi)007:1049: nad dang yams las grol ba dang //
NK033(gi)007:1050: dbang rtags 'di nyid btags pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1051: lam chen lnga po bsten par gyis //
NK033(gi)007:1052: rdo rje'i don dang 'bral ba med pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:1053: yang dag sa la de bzhin gnas pa dang //
NK033(gi)007:1054: gsang sngags kun gyi dgongs pa lon par shog /
NK033(gi)007:1055: badz+ra tsan+da sarba ha sa na h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1056: so so'i gsang mtshan nas bos la /
NK033(gi)007:1058: las kyi rigs kyi gsang mtshan gang yin pa //
NK033(gi)007:1059: sems dpa' las kyi rigs rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)007:1060: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1062: rin chen rigs kyi gsang mtshan gang yin pa //
NK033(gi)007:1063: sems dpa' rin chen rigs rnams kyis //
NK033(gi)007:1065: pad+ma rigs kyi sems dpa' pad+ma rigs skal ldan 'di la h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1066: rdo rje rigs kyi gsang sems dpa' rdo rje'i rigs skal ldan h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1067: de bzhin rigs kyi gsang sems dpa' de bzhin rigs rnams skal ldan h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1068: de la sogs te bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)007:1069: gsang mtshan dam pa gang yin pa //
NK033(gi)007:1076: de ltar tshig dang mthun par bsgom zhing dbang bskur bas /
NK033(gi)007:1077: dngos grub chen po thob par 'gyur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1078: bkra shis kyang brjod par bya'o ////
NK033(gi)007:1079: de nas tshe dbang rin po che bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1080: dkyil 'khor spyi mthun ltar bris pa'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)007:1081: bum pa mgul chings dmar po dkar gsum gyis bkang ba 'bru'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol zhing /
NK033(gi)007:1082: 'bras chan dang sha mar bu ram sogs zhim pa sna tshogs bkod /
NK033(gi)007:1083: bum pa'i steng du tshe'i 'brang rgyas zas ro zhim pas brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)007:1084: mda' rgod sgro ma la dar sna me long gis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)007:1085: gzungs thag dmar po sum sgril btags la /
NK033(gi)007:1087: dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs mtshams su mda' bzhi gri bzhi sogs rgyan bkod pas brgyan par byas la /
NK033(gi)007:1089: bdag dbang chen gyi ting nge 'dzin brtan pa'i ngang
NK033(gi)007:1090: nas yi ge n+ri 'od gsal ba las 'od zer
NK033(gi)007:1091: 'phros / sangs rgyas byang sems grangs med pa 'od
NK033(gi)007:1092: kyi gong bur dkyil 'khor rdzas dang bcas pa la
NK033(gi)007:1093: 'phros / thim par bsam / yi ge +aahdzaba tu bgrang /
NK033(gi)007:1094: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1095: bdag nyid dpal chen du gsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)007:1096: slob ma tshe dpag med du gsal ba'i bar du +aahdakara po dgu las 'od zer 'phros /
NK033(gi)007:1097: +aaha zhes pas 'od zer dmar po grangs med pa 'phros te /
NK033(gi)007:1098: slob ma'i lus la thim pas tshe thob par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:1100: rdo rje spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1102: +aahde dag kyang tshe dpag med sku mdog dmar po sha stag tu sgom /
NK033(gi)007:1104: tshe dpag med sku mdog sku stod ser po //
NK033(gi)007:1105: lte ba man chad ljang gu /
NK033(gi)007:1106: phyag mtshan g.yas tshe'i bum pa /
NK033(gi)007:1107: g.yon rin pa che 'od 'bar ba bsnams par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:1110: a pa ri mi ta +aa yur+dz+ny+aa na badz+ra d+h+ri kra dzahh+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1112: +aahdang dbyer med du gnas bar sgom //
NK033(gi)007:1113: de nas tshe 'gugs par bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1115: shar lho nub byang dbus lnga nas //
NK033(gi)007:1116: tshe bdag rigs lnga lha mo'i tshogs //
NK033(gi)007:1117: sku mdog sna lnga 'bar ba la //
NK033(gi)007:1118: chibs su 'byung ba lnga la bcibs //
NK033(gi)007:1119: phyag na tshe yi bum pa bsnams //
NK033(gi)007:1120: phyogs bzhi dbus lnga'i sgo phyes la //
NK033(gi)007:1121: bdud rtsi tshe yi dngos grub stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1122: tshe mchog dkyil 'khor dbab tu gsol //
NK033(gi)007:1123: zhes tshe bkug cing dkyil 'khor gyi tshe rdzas la bstims nas /
NK033(gi)007:1124: bum pa tshe'i 'brang rgyas sogs slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1126: bcom ldan tshe dpag med pa ni //
NK033(gi)007:1127: sku la tshe yi ber chen gsol //
NK033(gi)007:1128: phyag na tshe yi longs spyod bsnams //
NK033(gi)007:1129: zhal nas tshe yi longs spyod 'gyed //
NK033(gi)007:1130: tshe dang longs spyod rgyas par mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:1131: skal ldan 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1132: dbang gi dkyil 'khor bstan du gsol //
NK033(gi)007:1133: lo brgya 'tsho dang ston brgya btsa' //
NK033(gi)007:1134: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi //
NK033(gi)007:1135: dngos grub chen po thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:1139: pad+ma +aa yur+dz+ny+aa na +aah karmah+aa yur+dz+ny+aa na h+aum h+r+aih zhes dbang bskur zhing bkra shis brjod la /
NK033(gi)007:1141: 'gyur med tshe'i dbang thob par 'gyur ro ////
NK033(gi)007:1142: de nas rig pa rang gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1143: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi sgo bzhi mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i dbus /
NK033(gi)007:1144: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad shin tu mdzes pa dang /
NK033(gi)007:1145: kha bye ba dang ma bye ba spel ma'i pad+ma'i d+r+wa ba dang /
NK033(gi)007:1146: de'i phyi rim zlum po bum pa'i dbyibs can /
NK033(gi)007:1147: tshogs gtor yang gong dang mthun /
NK033(gi)007:1148: dkyil 'khor dbus su rma bya'i sgro dang /
NK033(gi)007:1151: phyi rol du pad+ma'i steng du byang sems dmar po dang /
NK033(gi)007:1153: rang pad+ma he ru ka gong ltar gsal ba'i ngang nas +aahbazlasa shing /
NK033(gi)007:1154: slob bu yang pad+ma he ru kar bsgom zhing ye shes pa /
NK033(gi)007:1155: rdo rje dang bcas tish+tha badz+rasa brtan par byas /
NK033(gi)007:1156: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi sgrub rdzas slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1159: dag pas dag pa'i rgyu mtshan de //
NK033(gi)007:1160: gsang bas gsang ba'i 'od ldan pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1161: chos sku lhun rdzogs bde ba che //
NK033(gi)007:1162: stong nyid rang gsal bde bar bskur //
NK033(gi)007:1163: ma h+aa a nu pra ti ya a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK033(gi)007:1164: zhes rma bya'i sgro chun gyis dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1166: chos nyid gsal 'tsher g.yos pa med //
NK033(gi)007:1167: rdo rje skyon bral byang chub sems //
NK033(gi)007:1168: bdud rtsi dag pas chos nyid sku //
NK033(gi)007:1170: bo d+hi tsit+ta ab+hi shiny+tsa ahah zhes byang sems dkar pos dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1172: 'khor ba'i skyon spangs ye shes dmar //
NK033(gi)007:1173: 'dod chags chos spangs chos nyid kyis //
NK033(gi)007:1174: chags med ye shes pad+ma gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1175: ldan b+ha ga stong nyid de /
NK033(gi)007:1176: bdag med snying po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1177: su man rtsa su r+aa ga h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1178: zhes byang sems dmar pos dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1179: khro bo'i sku dpral ba sogs gnas bzhir bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1181: dpa' gtum rdo rje'i rang bzhin las //
NK033(gi)007:1183: rang gsal chos nyid me long sku //
NK033(gi)007:1185: 'gyur med dbyings su dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1186: kro ta a nu ya h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1188: zhes dbang gnas bzhir bskur zhing bkra shis brjod //
NK033(gi)007:1189: de nas bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang bskur ni /
NK033(gi)007:1190: dkyil 'khor dbus zlum po rdo rje'i ra ba gru bzhi sgo bzhi'i mtshams bzhir bum pa bzhi /
NK033(gi)007:1191: phyi rim zlum pol dkyil 'khor spyi ltar bris /
NK033(gi)007:1192: de'i dbus su bum pa kha brgyan dang bcas te bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1194: dri zhim gyi chus kha gdong bkrus la /
NK033(gi)007:1195: bdag dang slob bu pad+ma he ru kar bsgoms la /
NK033(gi)007:1197: rol mo dang bcas ye shes pa dbab /
NK033(gi)007:1198: rdo rje dang bcas pas tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK033(gi)007:1201: chags med ye shes dri ma med /
NK033(gi)007:1202: rnam dag 'od gsal shes rab thabs //
NK033(gi)007:1203: sku gsum shes rab 'byung ba'i thabs //
NK033(gi)007:1204: byang chub sems las sprul sku 'gyed //
NK033(gi)007:1205: chos nyid rtog med rdzas bzhi ste //
NK033(gi)007:1206: gnyis 'das chos skur dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1207: su la badz+ra pra ti ti ha ha +aah man shel /
NK033(gi)007:1208: byang chub snying po stong pa'i rgyud //
NK033(gi)007:1209: sku gsum ngo bo nyid las ni //
NK033(gi)007:1210: ye shes ma skyes rab rdzogs pas //
NK033(gi)007:1211: gzhan nas btsal bar mi bya ste //
NK033(gi)007:1212: rang nyid lha yi lhar gyur mchog /
NK033(gi)007:1214: stong pa chen por dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1215: swa b+h+aa wa a ta ri shwa sa la b+hi h+aum +aah thig le rnam lnga /
NK033(gi)007:1217: chos sku rtogs las 'das pa ni //
NK033(gi)007:1218: bsam 'das brjod med ngo bo stong //
NK033(gi)007:1219: rang nyid rdzogs chen lhun grub pas //
NK033(gi)007:1220: thig le gcig par dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1221: ahb+hi s+t+wam b+ha ya +aah man shel /
NK033(gi)007:1223: e ma ngo mtshar rmad byung ba //
NK033(gi)007:1224: stong pa'i snying po 'od gsal ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1225: ma chags gos med byang chub sems //
NK033(gi)007:1226: dri med dag pa'i rig snang ste //
NK033(gi)007:1227: rdzogs chen mtha' dang dbus med pas //
NK033(gi)007:1228: snang ba bzhi rdzogs dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1229: ba la rat+na la ma h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1232: chos sku stong pa nyid kyi ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1233: rang byung ye shes rtog med dbyings //
NK033(gi)007:1234: stong gsal rig pa'i snying por ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1235: stong nyid bdag med ye shes dang //
NK033(gi)007:1236: chos rnams lhun grub rdzogs chen pa //
NK033(gi)007:1237: yang dag ye shes 'od gsal ba //
NK033(gi)007:1238: stong pa nyid du dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1242: de nas gsang dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1243: slob ma gsum mam lnga las mi mang bar byas /
NK033(gi)007:1244: dbang rten phyag rgya mtshan nyid ldan pa /
NK033(gi)007:1245: dung can ri mo ha ri'i rigs bzhi tshang na rab /
NK033(gi)007:1246: de ma byung yang mtshan nyid dang ldan pa zhig btsal la /
NK033(gi)007:1249: mu khud 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad rnams phyogs tshon dang mdzes tshon du byas /
NK033(gi)007:1250: dbus kyi lte bar rnam snang mngon byang gi sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1251: de'i steng du snang ba mtha' yas //
NK033(gi)007:1252: de'i gtsug tu pad+ma dbang chen gyi sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1253: de'i steng du rma bya'i gdugs dar gyis brgyan pa phub /
NK033(gi)007:1254: slob dpon kha shar nas nub tu bltas la /
NK033(gi)007:1255: dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor bkra shis kyi bum pa kha rgyan dang bcas pa bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1256: lha'i mdun du me long mdzes pa bkram /
NK033(gi)007:1257: shar phyogs kyi cha la thod pa'i nang du byang sems dmar po bsham /
NK033(gi)007:1258: byang gi cha la me long yu ba can /
NK033(gi)007:1259: de'i nang du byangs sems dkar po /
NK033(gi)007:1260: lho'i cha la bu ma skyes pa'i bud med kyi tshil bu sha dang mar me rnams bkod /
NK033(gi)007:1261: de nas gsang yum chas su zhugs pa /
NK033(gi)007:1262: bye ru sogs rin po che'i rgyan gyis spras pa shar du bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1263: de bzhin du gzhan rig ma gsum yang phyogs bzhir bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1264: slob dpon pad+ma he ru ka'i bskyed rim du zhugs la /
NK033(gi)007:1266: phyag rgya rnams kyis dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing /
NK033(gi)007:1268: de nas slob dpon la zhal skyems drangs shing gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK033(gi)007:1271: mkha' gsang gnyis sprod dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1272: shes rab thabs ldan sbyor sgrol dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1273: dpa' bo chen pos bka' stsol zhig /
NK033(gi)007:1274: dbang bdag rdo rje 'dzin rgyal sku //
NK033(gi)007:1275: ma rig rmugs pa'i mig ldan pas //
NK033(gi)007:1276: shes rab mig gi dbang bskur stsol /
NK033(gi)007:1277: rmugs shing myos pas sgra ma thos //
NK033(gi)007:1278: gnyis med snyan gyi dbang stsol zhig /
NK033(gi)007:1279: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1280: rnam dag 'od gsal dri ma tshor //
NK033(gi)007:1281: ye shes shangs kyi dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1282: phyi nang yul la chags gyur pas //
NK033(gi)007:1284: chos nyid dag pa'i ro ma myong //
NK033(gi)007:1285: rang rig bcud ldan dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1286: phyi nang yul la chags gyur pas //
NK033(gi)007:1287: dbyings dang rigs pa'i gzugs ma mthong //
NK033(gi)007:1288: 'od gsal lus kyi dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1289: dran pa kun tu mtshon byed pa //
NK033(gi)007:1290: rang snang snying po'i don ma rtogs //
NK033(gi)007:1291: lta ba rig pa'i dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:1294: de nas slob bu pad+ma he ru ka yab yum du gsal ba la /
NK033(gi)007:1297: de nas dbang chen gyi yum slob dpon gyi g.yon phyogs su bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1299: dang po rdzas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1300: rnam snang mngon byang gi sku spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1302: ye shes rnam dag 'od snang chos sku'i dbyings //
NK033(gi)007:1303: skye med rang gsal thugs rje'i dbyings las byang chub sems //
NK033(gi)007:1304: dri med skyon bral rig pa zhi ba'i yab //
NK033(gi)007:1305: stong pa nyid mtshon rgyu las byang chub sems //
NK033(gi)007:1306: 'khor la mi gnas rang snang sna tshogs 'phro //
NK033(gi)007:1307: dag pa'i rgyu mtshan bde ba'i thig le ste //
NK033(gi)007:1308: chags la chags dga' bde ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1309: sarba d+har+m+aa rat+na tsakra +aah snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku /
NK033(gi)007:1311: stong nyid dmar mdangs shes rab dbang gi sku //
NK033(gi)007:1312: chos nyid mkha' mnyam snang srid shes rab yum //
NK033(gi)007:1313: gsang sngags las byung thig le 'dren byed ma //
NK033(gi)007:1314: rak+ta'i rang bzhin chos nyid 'dren byed ma //
NK033(gi)007:1315: shes rab dril nas sku yi snang ba gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1316: b+ha ga'i dbyings nas sprul sku dus gsum 'byung //
NK033(gi)007:1317: 'gag med chags nyams bde ba skyed par byed //
NK033(gi)007:1318: yi ge mum dang ldan pa'i rigs su snang //
NK033(gi)007:1319: dbang rtags 'od zer rdo rje le brgan 'phro //
NK033(gi)007:1320: rtog med shes rab dbyings kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1321: mu sa r+aa ga la h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1322: pad+ma dbang chen gyi sku bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1324: skye med ro ldan m+aam sa tshil chen bcas //
NK033(gi)007:1325: rgyal ba kun dang skye med snying po mnyam //
NK033(gi)007:1326: rig pa'i sku dang so sor tha mi dad //
NK033(gi)007:1327: dbyings dang mi 'bral shes rab thabs dang ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1328: sgo lnga ma 'gags zhi gnas lhag mthong ste //
NK033(gi)007:1329: bskyed pa ma yin rang byung rdzogs pa che //
NK033(gi)007:1330: sna tshogs 'od 'phro longs sku nyid kyi lus //
NK033(gi)007:1331: ma sgrib dri med shes rab ye shes can //
NK033(gi)007:1332: gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin thugs mchog tsit+ta'i ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1333: mi dmigs stong gsal grags stong gnyis las 'das //
NK033(gi)007:1334: gnyis 'dzin yul 'das chos nyid dag pa'i snyan //
NK033(gi)007:1335: 'khor ba'i skyon spangs ye shes dri zhim shangs //
NK033(gi)007:1336: the tshom gnyis gsal pad+ma dag pa'i ljags //
NK033(gi)007:1337: skye ba rgyun bcad ye shes sku gsum tshul //
NK033(gi)007:1338: ma skyes thig le'i ngang du dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1339: a yang pu ti ta a h+aum +aah rma bya'i sgro chun /
NK033(gi)007:1341: stong pa nyid dang nam mkha'i sku mtshon te //
NK033(gi)007:1342: stong nyid 'gags med mtha' nyid rnam par gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1343: rgya ma chad pa'i ye shes bum pa'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:1344: stong nyid dbyings zlum ye shes thig le'i ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1345: rgyud gsang rmad byung sku ni du mas stong //
NK033(gi)007:1346: mtha' dang dbus med yangs pa snying po'i don //
NK033(gi)007:1347: rang snang chos nyid ye nas gzung 'dzin bral //
NK033(gi)007:1348: chos nyid las ni sku nyid so sor gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1349: yang gsang don ston kha rgyan snying por bcas //
NK033(gi)007:1350: dag pa nyid kyis dag pa nyid ston sku //
NK033(gi)007:1351: bum pa'i gzugs la sku bzhi'i ye shes gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1352: sku gsum stong pa'i mtha' gnyis rang snang ste //
NK033(gi)007:1353: thabs mkhas ye shes sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK033(gi)007:1354: tshig dang brjod bya gnyis las rab tu 'das //
NK033(gi)007:1355: sangs rgyas dang ni rig pa stong nyid gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1356: ye shes dang ni sku yang ma bsgribs gsal //
NK033(gi)007:1357: chos nyid rang byung rtog med pas //
NK033(gi)007:1358: mkha' klong dbyings su dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1359: la ma du ya spri ta h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1361: de ltar rdzas kyi dbang bskur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1362: yang dag dbang la 'jug tshe na //
NK033(gi)007:1363: g.yon gyi yum la dmigs byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1364: byang chub sems gnyis 'dren pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:1365: b+ha ga'i nang du ril bu gzhug /
NK033(gi)007:1366: phyed brten na ni nas gcig ste //
NK033(gi)007:1367: lhag ma med par rdzogs byed na //
NK033(gi)007:1368: che chung sran ma'i tshad dang mnyam //
NK033(gi)007:1369: des ni gnyis ka 'dren par byed //
NK033(gi)007:1370: thig le zlog par byed pa na //
NK033(gi)007:1371: yi ge b+h+r+aum bzhi dran par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1372: dmar po rang la bstim byed na //
NK033(gi)007:1374: de ltar dran zhing gsal byas na //
NK033(gi)007:1376: ril bu bcug la sbyar bya ste //
NK033(gi)007:1377: dkyil 'khor nub kyi phyogs dag tu //
NK033(gi)007:1378: sgrub pa yab yum skul byed pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1379: sbyor ba'i brda yis 'di skad gsungs //
NK033(gi)007:1380: hoh bdag nyid las ni sna tshogs snang //
NK033(gi)007:1381: rgyal ba thams cad mnyam sbyar bas //
NK033(gi)007:1382: mkha' la sems dpa' 'od du zhu //
NK033(gi)007:1385: mnyam par sbyor cig rdo rje rgyal //
NK033(gi)007:1387: bde dga' longs spyod chos kyi sku //
NK033(gi)007:1388: gnyis med dbyings su brda sbyor 'khyud //
NK033(gi)007:1389: m+aum ah bde ldan phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:1390: rdo rje la ni bstim pa ste //
NK033(gi)007:1392: sdoms shig stong nyid mu dra ste //
NK033(gi)007:1393: bstims shig byang chub dbyings su stims //
NK033(gi)007:1395: de nas slob bu dad ldan gyis //
NK033(gi)007:1396: me long ma chag ma gas pas //
NK033(gi)007:1397: byang chub sems ni lce yis blang //
NK033(gi)007:1398: blangs te slob dpon nyid la phul //
NK033(gi)007:1399: de nas slob dpon gsang ba nyid //
NK033(gi)007:1400: 'gying po'i chas su zhugs nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1401: bu la gnang ba'i skabs phye ste //
NK033(gi)007:1402: sta gon cho ga rdzogs byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1403: dang po spyi gtsug dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1405: bu yi steng du bzhag pa'i tshe //
NK033(gi)007:1406: rdzas de yi ge h+aum du bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1408: yi ge de la rab bsnan te //
NK033(gi)007:1410: de nas tshangs pa'i bu gar thim //
NK033(gi)007:1411: dung khang 'bar bar babs par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1413: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mgo la bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1414: de nas chos nyid rtsar thim pas //
NK033(gi)007:1415: h+aum de 'od kyi thig ler bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1416: de nas tsit+tara thim par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1417: h+aum de sna tshogs 'od du zhu //
NK033(gi)007:1418: de nyid las ni zhi skur bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1419: thugs la dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bsgom //
NK033(gi)007:1420: de nas yi ge h+aum de yang //
NK033(gi)007:1421: sgal tshigs nyid kyi rtar brgyud nas //
NK033(gi)007:1422: pho mo gang yin gsang gnas su //
NK033(gi)007:1423: yi ge de nyid bab par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1424: brgyud pa'i dbang nyid ma rdzogs par //
NK033(gi)007:1425: yig ge de nyid rtag par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1426: de ltar bab lugs rnam bzhi bsgom //
NK033(gi)007:1427: de ltar ting 'dzin gsal byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1428: byang chub sems nyid snod de yang //
NK033(gi)007:1429: bu mchog dad dang ldan pa yi //
NK033(gi)007:1430: gsang ba'i gnas su rdzas bzhag ste //
NK033(gi)007:1431: byang chub sems de m+aum dang +aah de nyid 'od du 'phros pa las //
NK033(gi)007:1432: byang chub sems ni 'od du bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1434: gsang ba'i mkha' la thim par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1435: h+aum dang gnyis med 'brel bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1436: gnyis med yi ge de dag ni //
NK033(gi)007:1437: yam gis sgo yang rtsar bskyod nas //
NK033(gi)007:1438: lte ba'i rtsa la thim par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1439: de nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK033(gi)007:1440: gang dag skye med 'dod pa rnams //
NK033(gi)007:1441: yi ge de yi byin rlabs nas //
NK033(gi)007:1442: skye ba'i sgo yang chod par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1443: gang dag bu dang tsha 'dod pa //
NK033(gi)007:1444: de yi 'od dang zer ldan pas //
NK033(gi)007:1445: dbang po'i dwangs ma mig tu bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1446: de las sha gzugs dod par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1447: de las yan lag rgyas par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1448: srid pa'i sha gzugs dod pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:1449: de nas tsit+tara brgyud par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1450: zhi ba'i sku la thim gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1451: sku rnams 'od dang ldan gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1452: yab yum sbyor ba byas par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1454: lte ba'i sras la dbang bskur bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1455: de nas yam gis bskyod nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1456: chos nyid sad pa'i gzhi rtsar gyur //
NK033(gi)007:1458: dwangs ma gnyis su phye gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1460: yam gis dung khang nang du bskyod //
NK033(gi)007:1461: de las 'od zer lnga byung bas /
NK033(gi)007:1462: khro bo'i sku rnams 'od ldan bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1463: h+aum dang +aah gnyis rnam dag pas //
NK033(gi)007:1464: khro bo yab yum sbyor bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1465: de nyid thig le'i sems sbyar bas //
NK033(gi)007:1466: byang chub sems ni 'od du zhu //
NK033(gi)007:1467: de nas h+aum gis mar brdas nas //
NK033(gi)007:1468: srog pa rtsa yi rtar brgyud nas //
NK033(gi)007:1469: lte ba'i sras la dbang bskur bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1470: thig le de la bstim nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1471: h+aum de slar la log par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1472: h+aum las sgra dang 'od byung bas //
NK033(gi)007:1473: bu yi tshangs pa'i bu ga na //
NK033(gi)007:1474: h+aum nyid 'od dang bcas par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1476: m+aum nyid rna ba g.yas g.yon no //
NK033(gi)007:1477: de ltar yi ge 'bru gsal te //
NK033(gi)007:1478: spyi gtsug h+aum nyid chos skur bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1480: yab yum bcas par rab tu bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1481: byang chub sems nyid bcas pa las //
NK033(gi)007:1482: bu yi lus la thim gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1483: lus nyid 'od du zhu bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1484: de nas stong nyid chos skur bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1485: chos sku'i sras nyid yang dag bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1487: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1488: yab yum grangs med 'phro bsam ste //
NK033(gi)007:1489: dzah h+aum bam hoh'i brdas bskul nas //
NK033(gi)007:1490: las kyi phyag rgya legs bsdams te //
NK033(gi)007:1491: yab yum gnyis med bde ba las //
NK033(gi)007:1492: mkha' la byang chub sems bcas pas //
NK033(gi)007:1493: lus dang dbang po tshim byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1494: lus rnams 'od du zhu gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1495: longs spyod sku dang dbyer med bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1496: longs sku'i sras su gyur par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1497: de nas m+aum las dmigs byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1498: m+aum nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK033(gi)007:1499: sprul sku rdo rje 'dzin du bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1500: de nyid 'od du zhu ba las //
NK033(gi)007:1501: rnams snang mngon byang yab yum bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1502: dzahh+aum bam hoh'i brdas bskul bas //
NK033(gi)007:1503: las kyi phyag rgyas bsdams gyur pas //
NK033(gi)007:1504: yab yum gnyis med sbyor bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1506: bu yi lus la thim gyur nas //
NK033(gi)007:1507: lus ni 'od du zhu nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1508: dbang rdzogs mngon shes drug ldan pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1509: sprul sku nyid kyi sku thob ste //
NK033(gi)007:1510: sprul sku rdo rje'i sras dbang thob //
NK033(gi)007:1511: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang chos sku thob //
NK033(gi)007:1512: de ltar dbang nyid rab rdzogs nas //
NK033(gi)007:1513: brgyud pa rnam pa de bzhin no //
NK033(gi)007:1514: de la sku gsum rdzogs pa'i dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1515: rang byung dbang nyid rab tu rdzogs //
NK033(gi)007:1516: sku gsum dbyer med rdzogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:1517: dbang bskur dkyil 'khor rdzogs byed nas //
NK033(gi)007:1518: dbang po sbyor ba byed tshe na //
NK033(gi)007:1519: bdag dang sgrub pa'i yum nyid kyi //
NK033(gi)007:1520: spyi gtsug bde ba'i gnas su yang //
NK033(gi)007:1521: yi ge 'di ltar bsgom par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1522: yum la m+aum nyid dmar po ste //
NK033(gi)007:1525: tshangs pa'i bu gar thim par bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1526: de gnyis 'od du zhu ba las //
NK033(gi)007:1527: sa ma ya zhes sgra byung nas //
NK033(gi)007:1528: dam tshig phyag rgya 'khyud nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1529: yab yum gnyis med sbyor bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1530: mkha' la byang chub sems bab pas //
NK033(gi)007:1531: rtsa bzhi'i na nga du thig le stong //
NK033(gi)007:1533: thig le dwangs snyigs bye nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1534: dwangs ma 'od zer lnga rnams te //
NK033(gi)007:1535: snyigs ma dkar po thig le'o //
NK033(gi)007:1536: dwangs ma tsit+ta'i nang du babs //
NK033(gi)007:1538: dwangs ma yi ti'i sgra byung bas //
NK033(gi)007:1539: zhi ba yab yum sgras bskul te //
NK033(gi)007:1540: chos kyi phyag rgyas 'khyud nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1541: yab yum gnyis med sbyor bar bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1542: byang chub sems nyid babs pa las //
NK033(gi)007:1544: cha shas 'od zer thams cad kyang //
NK033(gi)007:1545: sgal tshigs thig le dag la thim //
NK033(gi)007:1546: las kyi rlung gis ded nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1547: sgal tshigs dag pa'i rta brgyud la //
NK033(gi)007:1548: gsang ba'i mkha' la bab gyur te //
NK033(gi)007:1549: bdag nyid sbyor ba'i brdas bskul te //
NK033(gi)007:1550: las kyi phyag rgyas 'khyud byas nas //
NK033(gi)007:1551: yum gyis drangs shing bde ba skye //
NK033(gi)007:1552: yab yum gnyis med lhan sbyar te //
NK033(gi)007:1553: bde gsang chos kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1554: snying po'i sku yang des 'thob bo //
NK033(gi)007:1555: dang po'i skabs su shes par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1556: de ltar dbang bskur rdzogs nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1557: sbyor ba'i dbang bskur 'di ltar brjod //
NK033(gi)007:1558: rigs nges bstan pa'i tshig 'di brjod //
NK033(gi)007:1560: 'di ni rigs nges rgyal ba'i sras //
NK033(gi)007:1561: ha e ma hoh de ring phan chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK033(gi)007:1562: da ni sangs rgyas nges pa'i lam //
NK033(gi)007:1563: sku gsum 'bras bu rang snang ste //
NK033(gi)007:1564: phyin ci ma log dbang thob nas //
NK033(gi)007:1565: sangs rgyas sku dang dbyer med mnyam //
NK033(gi)007:1566: rdzogs sangs rgyas pa'i sku thob nas //
NK033(gi)007:1567: phyir mi ldog pa'i sa yang thob //
NK033(gi)007:1568: gdod nas ma chags snying po'i don //
NK033(gi)007:1569: snga ma khyod kyis ma thob ste //
NK033(gi)007:1571: de ring phan chad rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK033(gi)007:1572: yang dag nges pa'i sa thob pas //
NK033(gi)007:1573: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK033(gi)007:1574: thig le nyag gcig dbang thob bo //
NK033(gi)007:1575: lnga gsum rgyud dang rdzogs pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:1576: rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob pas //
NK033(gi)007:1577: de la lhun gyis gnas par brjod //
NK033(gi)007:1578: bdag nyid sras su byung nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1579: sangs rgyas nyid kyang mnyes pa yin //
NK033(gi)007:1580: rab tu dgyes pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK033(gi)007:1583: +aahldana byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkar //
NK033(gi)007:1584: m+aum ldan byang sems dmar dwangs 'od zer 'phros //
NK033(gi)007:1585: gnyis med sku yang rab tu gsal ba'i thig le ste //
NK033(gi)007:1586: sku gsum yon tan byang chub sems mnyam pas //
NK033(gi)007:1587: byang chub snying po rgyud la lhun grub sku //
NK033(gi)007:1588: tha dad mi 'byed chos sku stong bdag mo //
NK033(gi)007:1589: dkar dang dmar dang shes rab thabs mkhas sku //
NK033(gi)007:1590: stong nyid stong pa mkha' khyab kun la rol //
NK033(gi)007:1591: chags med chags pa'i tshul bstan byang chub nyid kyi rgyu //
NK033(gi)007:1592: mtshan ma spros bral gsang ba yum gyi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1593: thabs mkhas thugs rje chen po yin pas na //
NK033(gi)007:1594: deng nas bzung sde rgyal ba'i sras po'o //
NK033(gi)007:1595: bo d+hi tsit+ta a ni ga ya +aah bdud rtsi byin la /
NK033(gi)007:1596: e ma ngo mtshar lta ba'i dkyil 'khor che //
NK033(gi)007:1597: dkyil 'khor nyid la dkyil 'khor nyid bstan pa //
NK033(gi)007:1598: sngon chad ma 'tshal deng 'dir bdag gis shes //
NK033(gi)007:1599: rang gi rang bzhin yin par shes pa na //
NK033(gi)007:1600: gzhan nas ma btsal phyi nang dbang thob pas //
NK033(gi)007:1601: gsang ba'i dbang ni yongs rdzogs dus 'dir 'thob //
NK033(gi)007:1602: dpa' bos gnang bas bka' drin rab tu che'o //
NK033(gi)007:1603: ha ha he he rigs nges so //
NK033(gi)007:1606: dbang rdzogs yon kyang dbul bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:1607: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing bkra shis brjod //
NK033(gi)007:1608: de nas rdzogs chen rang snang gi dbang ni /
NK033(gi)007:1609: dkyil 'khor zlum po phyi rim 'khor los bskor ba /
NK033(gi)007:1610: sgo khor yug sogs spyi dang mthun /
NK033(gi)007:1611: dbus su rin po che'i bum pa kha rgyan mgul chings /
NK033(gi)007:1612: nang bum rdzas dang chus gang ba bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1613: de'i steng du rigs lnga'i sku rten tsaka li bsham /
NK033(gi)007:1614: shar gyi bum pa'i steng du rigs gsum gyi sku dang /
NK033(gi)007:1616: lho'i bum pa'i steng du rig pa gser phreng /
NK033(gi)007:1620: nub kyi bum pa'i khar khro chen rigs lnga'i sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1621: byang gi bum pa'i khar sgo ba bzhi'i sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1622: byang shar gyi bum pa'i steng du rigs gsum khro bo'i sku dang /
NK033(gi)007:1624: shar lho'i bum pa'i steng du rnam 'dzin dang /
NK033(gi)007:1626: kun tu bzang po'i sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1627: lho nub kyi bum pa'i steng du rigs lnga yum lnga'i sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1628: nub byang gi bum pa'i steng du kro ti shwa ri sogs khro mo yum lnga'i sku bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1629: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du bkra shis rdzas brgyad bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1630: bum pa re re'i rtsar phud dang bcas pa'i gtor ma re bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1631: ban+d+ha mtshan ldan nang du dam rdzas bsham /
NK033(gi)007:1632: bdag nyid pad+ma he ru kar gsal ba'i ngang nas +aahbargya rtsa brgyad bzlas /
NK033(gi)007:1633: slob ma pad+ma he ru kar gsal ba la ye shes pa spyan drangs shing bstim /
NK033(gi)007:1634: rol mo dang bcas rdo rje spyi bor bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1636: de nas bum pa zhi khro'i lha tshogs su gsal ba slob ma'i gnas lngar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1637: gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang nas /
NK033(gi)007:1639: lnga ldan rdo rje 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK033(gi)007:1640: rdo rje 'du 'bral med pa'i sku gsal ba //
NK033(gi)007:1641: gsang ldan rdo rje rigs kyis dbang bskur zhing //
NK033(gi)007:1642: rdo rje 'dus pa'i sras su dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1643: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+aan+tim kro d+ha shi bi
NK033(gi)007:1644: ra sa pa ri w+aa ra a b+hi shiny+tsa +aahh+aum
NK033(gi)007:1645: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes dbang bskur la /
NK033(gi)007:1647: gsang ba bde ldan rdo rje gar gyi bdag /
NK033(gi)007:1648: bdag dang gzhan dang sku lnga mthar phyin dang //
NK033(gi)007:1649: mi 'gyur gsal mchog dgyes pa'i gad mo che //
NK033(gi)007:1650: rig dang stong dang bya ba byed pa stobs //
NK033(gi)007:1651: chos la gnas pa'i sems dpa' yid la bskul //
NK033(gi)007:1652: zhes bum chus khrus bya zhing /
NK033(gi)007:1653: dbang rtags spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:1655: a la la hoh rdo rje mos pa rtsal /
NK033(gi)007:1664: e ma hoh ha hi srirba h+aum /
