NK033(gi)007:1665: rdo rje gsang mchog khyod dbang ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1666: dbang gi rigs ldan gsang mchog ste //
NK033(gi)007:1668: bde ldan dbyings mchog 'khor lo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1669: zhes sku rnams kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1670: phyogs bzhi'i bum pas rim pa bzhin /
NK033(gi)007:1672: chos nyid dbyings las rig pa'i dbyings shar ba //
NK033(gi)007:1673: mthong ba nyid dang ye shes thabs kyi sku //
NK033(gi)007:1674: tsit+ta rin chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK033(gi)007:1675: bde mchog thugs kyi 'khor lo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1679: bde ldan dbyings shar shes rab yum gyi ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1680: gsal 'tsher lhun sdug rdo rje rab gsang 'bar //
NK033(gi)007:1681: gsang ba mkha' dbyings b+ha ga'i gzhal yas su //
NK033(gi)007:1682: chos nyid spros bral bde chen dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1683: a a a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1685: rdo rje gsang ba bde mchog dbyings su sgrol //
NK033(gi)007:1686: shes rab mtha' ldan ka dag yangs pa'i ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1687: sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor sems dpa'i rang bzhin mchog /
NK033(gi)007:1688: chos rnams mi dmigs rdo rje sems dpa'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:1689: nam mkha' mtha' klas chos dbyings ro gcig tu //
NK033(gi)007:1690: las rnams mthar phyin stong nyid bde ba'i sku //
NK033(gi)007:1691: sems dang stong nyid chos kyi sku la dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1692: mchod ldan srid skyed lte ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK033(gi)007:1693: rdo rje las gsang thugs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1696: gsal ba rab skyed ye shes sems dpa'i ngang //
NK033(gi)007:1697: shes rab 'od 'phro nyon mongs zil gyis gnon //
NK033(gi)007:1698: rdo rje mda' 'phen shes rab dbyings su 'phen //
NK033(gi)007:1699: dkyil 'khor dbang sdud ye shes snang ba'i bdag /
NK033(gi)007:1700: sangs rgyas lnga ldan thugs kyi cod pan ldan //
NK033(gi)007:1701: rin chen thugs byed rtsa ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK033(gi)007:1702: mnyam nyid 'od 'phro chos sku'i dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1705: bde ldan thugs kyi gsang ba mchog /
NK033(gi)007:1706: yang gsang ye shes 'khor lo'i bdag /
NK033(gi)007:1707: gsang ldan dbyings nas ye shes 'od 'phro zhing //
NK033(gi)007:1708: phyogs med rang snang chos sku'i dkyil 'khor bdag /
NK033(gi)007:1709: bde ldan chos dbyings gsang bar dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1711: gsang sngags sku dang mtha' 'das dang //
NK033(gi)007:1712: sa rnams mthar phyin ye shes rnam par dag /
NK033(gi)007:1713: chos sku rang snang stong pa nyid du snang //
NK033(gi)007:1714: b+han+d+ha gsal 'phen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas dbyings //
NK033(gi)007:1715: rtog med bsam yas 'khor lo che ba'i chu //
NK033(gi)007:1716: rdo rje thugs kyi dbyings su dbang bskur ro //
NK033(gi)007:1718: de ltar tshig don rdzogs byas nas /
NK033(gi)007:1719: sngags dang phyag rgyas 'di ltar bstan //
NK033(gi)007:1720: mkhas pa ting 'dzin ldan pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1721: ting 'dzin sgo nas dbang bskur ba //
NK033(gi)007:1722: rnam snang mngon byang phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1723: spyi gtsug gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1725: bud+d+ha kra pa tsa h+aum h+aum b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:1727: mngon byang sku dang dbyer med bsam //
NK033(gi)007:1728: g.yas ni rdo rje gsor ba'i tshul //
NK033(gi)007:1729: g.yon ni dril bu dkrol ba'i tshul //
NK033(gi)007:1730: mgrin pa'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1733: lag mthil mnyam par bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1734: lte ba'i gnas su bzhag nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1735: de la yang ni 'di skad do //
NK033(gi)007:1737: pad+ma sarba kun len ha ha h+aum +aah lag gnyis mnyam par bzhag pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1738: dpral ba'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1741: krab+ha tsab h+r+aihh+r+aihh+r+aih g.yas pas ral gri'i tshul byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1742: g.yon pa thugs kar mnyam par bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1743: spyi bo'i gtsug tu bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1745: many+dzu badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aa h+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1746: lag gnyis 'khrig ma bsnol nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1747: sna tshogs rdo rje'i tshul du byas //
NK033(gi)007:1748: snying ga nyid du mnyam par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1750: na lam badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)007:1751: g.yas pa brkyangs te thugs ka ru //
NK033(gi)007:1752: thal mo skyabs sbyin gal du bzed //
NK033(gi)007:1753: g.yon pa brkyangs te de bzhin no //
NK033(gi)007:1754: snying gar dag tu bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1756: lag g.yas gur gyi tshul du byas //
NK033(gi)007:1757: spyi gtsug nyid du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1760: g.yas ba brdeg pa ltar byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1761: snying ga'i dbus su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1766: e a r+aa l+ai g+ha badz+ra sat+wa h+aum h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1767: rdo rje khu tshur bsnol ba la //
NK033(gi)007:1768: snying ga'i gnas su bzhag para bya //
NK033(gi)007:1770: pra dz+ny+aa sarba h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1771: a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rina chen sgrom bu ltar byas la /
NK033(gi)007:1772: gsang ba'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1774: badz+ra +aa yuhs+w+aa h+aa h+aum amh lag gnyis pad+ma ltar byas la /
NK033(gi)007:1775: snying ga'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1777: a mri ta du sa ha la h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)007:1778: g.yon pa'i sdigs mdzub phyag rgya ni //
NK033(gi)007:1779: lag pa'i mthil du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1781: a kro rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa a +aah g.yas pa se gol phyag rgya ni //
NK033(gi)007:1782: lte ba'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1784: h+ya g+r+ai wa sarba ku len sarba h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1785: lag gnyis khyung gshog ltar byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1786: smin phrag nyid du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1788: bud+d+ha kro d+ha sarba kra tsa ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1789: lag gnyis bum pa ltar byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1790: dpral ba'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1792: kun+da li a mri ta karma h+aum +aah lag gnyis srin lag mdzub sbyar la //
NK033(gi)007:1793: lce yi steng du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1795: badz+ra kri la t+ya sat+wa i se nyi h+aum h+aum phata /
NK033(gi)007:1796: g.yon pa lcags kyu'i phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1797: snying ga'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1799: dza sat+ye h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1800: lag gnyis zhags pa'i phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1801: mig ni g.yas su reg byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1803: badz+ra seng ha ya la ya b+hi ta ho ho hoh lag gnyis 'khyud brgyad sgrogs bsdams la //
NK033(gi)007:1804: dpung pa g.yon du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1806: mam du sa ya h+aum a hoh g.yas steng g.yon bskum khu tshur gyis //
NK033(gi)007:1807: snying ga nyid du brten byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1809: b+han d+ha badz+ra ka pa tsa h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1810: lag gnyis dgra s+t+wa'i phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1811: pus mo g.yon du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1813: ka la h+r+aihti ku len h+ye phatahphatahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1814: lag gnyis rta mgo'i phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1815: spyi bo'i gtsug tu bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1817: pad+ma ta kri ta h+aum kha la ya ha ha /
NK033(gi)007:1818: g.yas pa rtse gsum phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1819: lag gnyis bum pa ltar byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1820: spyi gtsug dag tu bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1822: tsan+da badz+ra p+aa ni e h+ye h+aum phatahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK033(gi)007:1823: lag gnyis gzhu 'gengs tshul byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1824: g.yon pa'i mdzub mo sna rtser bzhag /
NK033(gi)007:1826: badz+ra ku len ser ser h+aum h+aum ha /
NK033(gi)007:1827: lag g.yon lcags kyu'i phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1828: snying ga nyid du bzung byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1830: badz+ra dush+t+aa n+aa ga l+aa ya badz+ra h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1831: lag gnyis thod phreng phyag rgya yis //
NK033(gi)007:1832: spyi bo'i gtsug tu bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1833: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aah badz+ra many+dzu karma ta su d+ha h+aum h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1834: lag gnyis mnyam par bzhag pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1835: mgrin pa'i gnas su bzhag pa la //
NK033(gi)007:1837: sa ling sing h+aum +aah lag gnyis se gol bsnol ba yis //
NK033(gi)007:1838: rtsibs log g.yas su bzhag pa la //
NK033(gi)007:1840: ma byi sa rash+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK033(gi)007:1841: g.yas pa'i mtheb mos g.yon mdzub mnan //
NK033(gi)007:1842: rtsibs log g.yon du bzhag pa la //
NK033(gi)007:1844: lam h+r+aiha b+hi shiny+tsa +aah g.yas ni ral gri lta bu yis //
NK033(gi)007:1845: lce yi steng du bzhag pa la //
NK033(gi)007:1847: m+aum b+h+r+aum ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:1848: g.yas g.yon dag gi sor mo ni //
NK033(gi)007:1849: mtheb dang mdzub dang mathe'u chung sprad //
NK033(gi)007:1850: lhag ma gnyis ni bsgrengs bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:1851: g.yas pa thal mo gdengs pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1852: ltag pa'i khung du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1856: lag g.yas rtse gsum bsgrengs pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1857: rna ltag gnyis su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1859: badz+ra sun d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lag pa g.yas brkyangs mthe bong bsgrengs pa yis //
NK033(gi)007:1860: rna ltag g.yon du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1862: m+aum sh+ti a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lag g.yon mathe'u chung mdzub brkyangs te //
NK033(gi)007:1863: lkog ma'i gnas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1865: m+aum lam hang ti sa pa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lag gnyis pad+ma ltar byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1866: nu ma g.yas su bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1868: sa lang kro ti a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lag g.yon rtse bzhi ltar byas la //
NK033(gi)007:1869: 'tshog ma'i steng du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1871: bam sha ri a bi ti ni dzah+aah lag gnyis sor mo bsnol byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1872: spyi gtsug steng du bzhag par bya //
NK033(gi)007:1874: bish+ta stan d+ha sha ri a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah skyob pa mthar phyin sngags ldan pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1875: bde gshegs sku yi dbang bskur ni //
NK033(gi)007:1876: bkra shis gdugs la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1877: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1879: si pa ka ga y+aa sing a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah lta byed ma 'gags don mtshon pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1880: bde gshegs sku yi dbang bskur ni //
NK033(gi)007:1881: bkra shis nya la brten nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1882: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1884: swo ni sa ya su gu a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah smra byed pha rol sgra la mkhas //
NK033(gi)007:1885: sangs rgyas ljags kyi dbang bskur ni //
NK033(gi)007:1886: bkra shis pad+ma la brten nas //
NK033(gi)007:1887: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1889: ti ka ta ya sing a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah chos rnams las byung chos dbyings zlum //
NK033(gi)007:1890: sangs rgyas mgul gyi dbang bskur ni //
NK033(gi)007:1891: bkra shis bum pa la brten nas //
NK033(gi)007:1892: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1894: ti ta ka ta ga sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah mi nub rgyal mtshan chos kyi don //
NK033(gi)007:1895: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku yi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1896: bkra shis rgyal mtshan la brten nas //
NK033(gi)007:1897: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1899: pi shad de a yang a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah sgra dbyangs rtog med don mtshon pa'i //
NK033(gi)007:1900: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung gi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1901: bkra shis dung la brten byas nas //
NK033(gi)007:1902: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1904: sa tri yang ta mang a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah gsal 'dod ldan pa dpal be'u thugs //
NK033(gi)007:1905: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs kyi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1906: bkra shis dpal be'u la brten nas //
NK033(gi)007:1907: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1909: tsit+ta ya a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah thogs med myur mgyogs 'khor lo'i zhabs //
NK033(gi)007:1910: sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhabs kyi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:1911: bkra shis 'khor lo la brten nas //
NK033(gi)007:1912: deng mchog bu la gnang bar bgyi //
NK033(gi)007:1914: tsakra su lam b+hi na ku a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah dbang dang ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK033(gi)007:1915: dbang mchog rdzogs par byir byas nas //
NK033(gi)007:1916: dkyil 'khor thams cad legs byas te //
NK033(gi)007:1917: dpal ldan 'khor lo rdzogs byas nas //
NK033(gi)007:1918: bde ldan gsang mchog gsang ba'i dbyings //
NK033(gi)007:1919: yang gsang thugs kyi rdo rje mchog /
NK033(gi)007:1920: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK033(gi)007:1921: mkha' dang dbyangs ldan thams cad du //
NK033(gi)007:1922: bdag gi dbang mchog bskur ba bzhin //
NK033(gi)007:1923: deng nas bzung ste thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:1925: yang dag gsang ba'i don ldan te //
NK033(gi)007:1926: 'jig rten brten pa'i sku gsung thugs //
NK033(gi)007:1927: deng nas bzung la ma btang zhig /
NK033(gi)007:1928: e ma sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK033(gi)007:1929: rdo rje 'chang chen ma spang bar //
NK033(gi)007:1930: thugs kyi dkyil du legs par zungs //
NK033(gi)007:1931: a la la ho rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK033(gi)007:1932: bdag gis deng nas bzung nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1933: bskal pa brgya stong bar du yang //
NK033(gi)007:1934: bdag gis stong pa nyid kyi sku //
NK033(gi)007:1935: nam du yang ni mi btang ngo //
NK033(gi)007:1936: de ltar dbang rdzogs byas nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1937: phyag rgya sngags dang bcas pas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1938: sku yi rab tu bskul nas ni //
NK033(gi)007:1939: gsang sngags ldan pa rdzogs par byas //
NK033(gi)007:1940: ye gsang chen po 'di bshad pas //
NK033(gi)007:1941: thams cad rdzogs sangs rgyas sku thob //
NK033(gi)007:1942: de lta dbang rnams bskur nas /
NK033(gi)007:1944: ye d+ha r+m+aa bzlas pa sogs kyis bkra shis rgyas par brjod /
NK033(gi)007:1945: su pra tish+thasa brtan par byas /
NK033(gi)007:1946: dga' ston tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor /
NK033(gi)007:1947: de nas rjes kyi bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:1948: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la gtang rag gi mchod pa dang /
NK033(gi)007:1950: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad kha skong ba sogs rjes spyod spyi dang mthun par bya'o //
NK033(gi)007:1951: rgyud kyi dbang 'di nyid kun mkhyen chen po dri med 'od zer sku tshe'i stod la /
NK033(gi)007:1953: zhing gzhan du gzigs khar dbus pa d+har+m+aa bo b+hi
NK033(gi)007:1954: zhes pa zhig la dbang rgyun rnam dag 'dug pa
NK033(gi)007:1955: gzigs nas gsan te zhing la gshegs khar /
NK033(gi)007:1956: mkhas grub bde legs rgya mtsho rkyang pa la shin tu gsang ba'i tshul du gnang nas /
NK033(gi)007:1957: slar mdo khams phyogs su gcig brgyud du brgyud /
NK033(gi)007:1958: des kahthoga rdo rje 'bum la brgyud /
NK033(gi)007:1959: kahthoga rdo rje 'bum gyis dbus gtsang du byon nas /
NK033(gi)007:1960: bsam yas 'ja' stod du chos rje rin chen grub la gnang /
NK033(gi)007:1962: de'i dus phreng po nas bla ma pad+ma bzod pa la yang gcig brgyud kyi tshul du gnang 'dug /
NK033(gi)007:1964: slob ma dam ldan gsum las mang na /
NK033(gi)007:1965: bka' srung smug nag gis bka'i chad pa drag tu 'byung bas na /
NK033(gi)007:1966: bka' rgya 'di la shin tu dam par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)007:1967: dbang gi yig cha 'di zangs brag bla ma tshul
NK033(gi)007:1968: khrims rgyal mtshan gyis nan tan du bskul ba la
NK033(gi)007:1969: brten nas / rdzogs chen pa 'od gsal sgyu ma
NK033(gi)007:1970: gter bzhad rtsal gyis bkod pa'i yi ge pa ni
NK033(gi)007:1971: brten nas / / myang stod zangs brag bla ma tshul khrims rgyal mtshan gyis bgyis pa 'dis /
NK033(gi)007:1972: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i bstan pa mtha' dbus kun tu rgyas par shog /
NK033(gi)007:1974: 'di'i bka' srung khros ma'i dbang bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)007:1976: rtsa ba gsum la gus btud nas //
NK033(gi)007:1977: rdzogs pa chen po'i bka' srung che //
NK033(gi)007:1978: khros ma'i dbang bskur bri bar bya //
NK033(gi)007:1979: de yang gnas dben par dkyil 'khor gri khrag gis chag chag gdab /
NK033(gi)007:1980: e gru gsum mtha' me ris mtshan pa'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)007:1981: sa bon b+h+yo yig mthing nag gis mtshan pa /
NK033(gi)007:1982: de'i steng du many+dzi'i khar lcags sam thod pa'i nang du /
NK033(gi)007:1983: 'bru nag gi phye la dpal gtor brjid ldan sha khrag gis brgyan pa /
NK033(gi)007:1984: dar nag gi cod pan dang /
NK033(gi)007:1985: 'di nyid kyi sku rten tsaka lis brgyan pa'i mtha' bskor du /
NK033(gi)007:1986: phyi nang gi mchod pa spyan gzigs brjid ldan bshams la /
NK033(gi)007:1987: sngon 'gro spyi dang mthun par byas nas /
NK033(gi)007:1988: bdag nyid skad cig gis che mchog he ru kar
NK033(gi)007:1989: gsal ba'i mdun gyi gtor ma khros mar gsal ba
NK033(gi)007:1990: la / ye shes pa dgug cing bstim /
NK033(gi)007:1991: phyi nang gi mchod pas mchod cing bstod la /
NK033(gi)007:1993: ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:1995: h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum rag mo te ke ma tsa dza kha la b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:1996: ru lu ru lu ma ti b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:1998: bdag che mchog tu gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer sna lnga 'phros pas /
NK033(gi)007:2000: thams cad thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul //
NK033(gi)007:2001: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las thogs pa med par sgrub par bsam /
NK033(gi)007:2002: de nas slob ma khrus nas dbyung /
NK033(gi)007:2003: rdo rje slob dpon gyis yi dam gyi nga rgyal dang ldan pas bgegs bskrad /
NK033(gi)007:2005: slob bus man+dala phul la gsol ba gdab ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:2006: kye ma rdo rje 'dzin pa che //
NK033(gi)007:2007: skal ldan bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK033(gi)007:2008: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)007:2009: bka' srung khros ma'i dbang bskur stsol //
NK033(gi)007:2011: de nas slob dpon gyis slob ma la bdud rtsi byin la /
NK033(gi)007:2012: kun tu bzang mo'i thugs sprul te //
NK033(gi)007:2013: khros ma'i dbang bskur bu la sbyin //
NK033(gi)007:2014: dam tshig ma 'da' yun du srungs //
NK033(gi)007:2015: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2017: slob ma bsang chus bsangs la /
NK033(gi)007:2018: skad cig gis dur khrod me ri 'bar ba'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)007:2019: thod pa 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK033(gi)007:2020: rak+ta'i zham chu 'bab pa'i dbus su /
NK033(gi)007:2021: pad nyi dgra bgegs pho mo bsnol ba'i steng du
NK033(gi)007:2022: yi ge b+h+yo las 'od zer 'phro 'du yongs su
NK033(gi)007:2023: gyur pa las / bka' srung khros ma sku mdog mthing nag 'jig pa'i cha byad can /
NK033(gi)007:2024: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gangs ri ltar gtsigs pa /
NK033(gi)007:2025: ral pas sa gzhi khyab pa /
NK033(gi)007:2026: spyi bo'i gtsug tu mthing ral 'od du 'bar ba /
NK033(gi)007:2027: phyag g.yas bam gyi tsit+ta bsnams shing //
NK033(gi)007:2028: g.yon spyang mo khra thabs su thogs shing /
NK033(gi)007:2029: zhal du nyams pa'i snying khrag 'dren pa /
NK033(gi)007:2030: 'khor du lcags kyi spyang mo 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK033(gi)007:2031: ma mo 'bum gyi dbus na h+aum phata b+h+yo'i sgra 'brug ltar du sgrogs pa /
NK033(gi)007:2032: de'i gnas gsum gyi yi ge gsum dang /
NK033(gi)007:2033: khyad par thugs srog b+h+yo las 'od zer 'phros /
NK033(gi)007:2034: rang bzhin dang chos sku kun tu bzang mo'i klong nas /
NK033(gi)007:2035: rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgya mtsho la char
NK033(gi)007:2036: babs pa ltar byon nas dbyer du thim par bsam
NK033(gi)007:2037: la / ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:2038: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2039: rag mo te ke ma tsa dza kha la b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:2040: ru lu ru lu ma ti b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:2041: badz+ra +aa be sha ya a +aah dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis su med par bstims la /
NK033(gi)007:2043: de nas gtor ma de nyid phyi gtor ma'i rnam pa la /
NK033(gi)007:2044: nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang du bskyed
NK033(gi)007:2045: pa'i dbus su khros ma 'khor dang bcas pa bskyed
NK033(gi)007:2046: la / gtso 'khor rnams kyi dpral ba'i las 'od zer dkar po dang /
NK033(gi)007:2047: sku'i rnam pa dpag tu med pa slob mar thim par bsam /
NK033(gi)007:2048: gtor ma spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2050: kun tu bzang mo dbyings kyi ma mo che //
NK033(gi)007:2051: dam tshig can la dngos grub myur ster ma //
NK033(gi)007:2052: bstan pa'i zhing bcu'i srog rtsa gcod mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)007:2053: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i sku yi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:2054: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:2055: bstan pa'i dgra bo sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:2056: ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:2057: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2059: de nas gtor ma mgrin par bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2060: gtso 'khor rnams kyi mgrin pa'i +aahls 'od zer dmar po dang /
NK033(gi)007:2061: srog sngags lu gu rgyud kyi tshul du slob ma'i mgrin par thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:2063: kun tu bzang mo dbyings kyi ma mo mchog /
NK033(gi)007:2064: dam tshig can la dngos grub myur ster ma //
NK033(gi)007:2065: bstan pa'i dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)007:2066: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i gsung gi dbang //
NK033(gi)007:2067: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:2068: bstan pa'i dgra bo sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:2069: ma ma traka rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:2070: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2071: w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah de nas gtor ma snying khar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2072: gtso 'khor rnams kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer mthing ga dang /
NK033(gi)007:2073: thugs phyag mtshan gyi rnam pa slob ma'i snying gar thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:2075: kun tu bzang mo dbyings kyi ma mo mchog /
NK033(gi)007:2076: dam tshig can la dngos grub myur ster ma //
NK033(gi)007:2077: bstan pa'i dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)007:2078: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i thugs kyi dbang //

NK033(gi)007:2080: bstan pa'i dgra bo sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /

NK033(gi)007:2082: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2084: de nas gtor ma lte bar bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2085: gtso 'khor rnams kyi lte ba nas 'od zer ser po dang /
NK033(gi)007:2086: rin po che'i rnam pa dpag tu med pa byung nas /
NK033(gi)007:2087: slob bu'i lte bar thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:2089: kun tu bzang mo dbyings kyi ma mo che //
NK033(gi)007:2090: dam tshig can la dngos grub myur ster ma //

NK033(gi)007:2092: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i yon tan dbang //
NK033(gi)007:2093: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:2094: bstan pa'i dgra bo sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:2095: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i yon tan dbang //
NK033(gi)007:2096: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:2097: dgos 'dod yid bzhin 'grub pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK033(gi)007:2098: ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:2099: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2100: gu na a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa /
NK033(gi)007:2101: de nas gtor ma gsang gnas su bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2102: gtso 'khor rnams kyi gsang gnas nas 'od zer ljang gu dang /
NK033(gi)007:2103: las bzhi'i phyag mtshan gyi rigs dpag tu med pa byung nas /
NK033(gi)007:2104: slob ma'i gsang gnas su thim par bsam la /
NK033(gi)007:2106: kun tu bzang mo dbyings kyi ma mo che //
NK033(gi)007:2107: dam tshig can la dngos grub myur ster ma //
NK033(gi)007:2108: bstan pa'i dgra bo'i srog rtsa gcod mdzad ma //
NK033(gi)007:2109: bstan srung khros ma nag mo'i phrin las dbang //
NK033(gi)007:2110: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK033(gi)007:2111: mngon spyod drag po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK033(gi)007:2112: ma ma trag rak+sha kha mun tra /
NK033(gi)007:2113: mu ru mu ru mu h'u b+h+yo b+h+yo h'u /
NK033(gi)007:2115: de nas bzlas lung bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:2116: slob dpon che mchog he ru kar gsal ba dang /
NK033(gi)007:2117: slob bu khros mar gsal ba'i thugs kar rang rang
NK033(gi)007:2118: gi srog yig gi mthar sngags phreng gis bskor ba
NK033(gi)007:2119: las sngags phreng mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi
NK033(gi)007:2120: tshul du / slob dpon gyi zhal nas byung /
NK033(gi)007:2121: slob ma'i ngag la thim nas /
NK033(gi)007:2122: thugs ka'i sngags phreng la 'khod pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK033(gi)007:2126: mu ru mu ru mu h+aum b+h+yo b+h+yo h+aum /
NK033(gi)007:2127: rag mo te ke ma tsa dza kha la b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:2128: ru lu ru lu ma ting b+h+yo /
NK033(gi)007:2129: yim lim shim lim ma sha dzahmi sha dun dzahphoba ya /
NK033(gi)007:2139: tsi bo'i ru tra yag shi du ru ru /
NK033(gi)007:2142: zhes 'di'i rjes zlos byed du bcug /
NK033(gi)007:2143: bcom ldan bdag la stsal lags kyi //
NK033(gi)007:2144: bdag la 'go bar mdzad du gsol //
NK033(gi)007:2147: bcom ldan 'di la stsal lags kyi //
NK033(gi)007:2150: tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK033(gi)007:2151: de nas gtor ma slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK033(gi)007:2172: grub thob me long rdo rje /
NK033(gi)007:2175: mkhas grub bde legs rgya mtsho /
NK033(gi)007:2176: rta mgo bya bral chos rje /
NK033(gi)007:2182: sprul sku zhig po gling pa rnams kyi bka' dang dam las ma 'da' bar srung skyobs mdzod cig /
NK033(gi)007:2183: la sogs pas bka' bsgo dam bzhag rgyas par byas la /
NK033(gi)007:2185: de nas gtor ma dpag la dpal 'bar btsug /
NK033(gi)007:2186: sman raka bran la bskul ba bya ba ni /
NK033(gi)007:2188: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub //
NK033(gi)007:2189: gru gsum mthing nag klong dkyil na //
NK033(gi)007:2190: sngags kyi srung ma mthu mo che //
NK033(gi)007:2191: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK033(gi)007:2192: ral pa'i zar bus sa gzhi khebs //
NK033(gi)007:2193: g.yas pas zhing chen tsit+ta bsnams //
NK033(gi)007:2194: g.yon pas g.yu yi spyang mo bsnams //
NK033(gi)007:2197: mig gi dbang po mngon du phyungs //
NK033(gi)007:2198: lcags kyi sder chen 'bar ba yis //
NK033(gi)007:2199: lus kyi khong khrol snying phyungs shig /
NK033(gi)007:2201: srog rtsa snying rtsa chod la shog /
NK033(gi)007:2202: mgo dang lus su phrol la shog /
NK033(gi)007:2203: sha dang rus pa phyes la shog /
NK033(gi)007:2204: nang khrol dbang po nyul la shog /
NK033(gi)007:2205: dgra bo'i lha lnga dbang du bsdus //
NK033(gi)007:2206: mngon spyod drag pos rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)007:2207: zhe sdang bskyed la srid pa dkrugs //
NK033(gi)007:2208: mi mngon mkha' dbyings bde chen nas //
NK033(gi)007:2209: e dz+aa ti ral gcig ma //
NK033(gi)007:2210: dbu dgu thor gtsug gcig tu bcings //
NK033(gi)007:2211: khams gsum srid gsum dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)007:2212: deng 'dir las rnams thams cad byed //
NK033(gi)007:2213: mkha' la de bzhin gshog gcig ma //
NK033(gi)007:2214: dpal gyi gtsug 'byams a la la //
NK033(gi)007:2215: zangs kyi kha la lcags kyi so //
NK033(gi)007:2216: sna tshogs zhal du zhing 'gron ma //
NK033(gi)007:2217: mthing nag gcer bu dbu dgu ma //
NK033(gi)007:2218: snying yang dgu ste rkang gcig ma //
NK033(gi)007:2219: stong khams mchongs zhing mkha' la 'gro //
NK033(gi)007:2220: bltas pas bdud rnams sgrol bar byed //
NK033(gi)007:2221: gdug byed rnams kyi snying 'byin ma //
NK033(gi)007:2222: rdo rje ba spu re re la //
NK033(gi)007:2223: rdo rje lcags kyu re re ldan //
NK033(gi)007:2224: snang srid ma lus rdul du rlog /
NK033(gi)007:2225: bar bar mig nas khrag 'dzag ma //
NK033(gi)007:2226: rkan sgra rdeb cing bdud dpung 'joms //
NK033(gi)007:2227: rtag tu dbang phyug sku la 'khril //
NK033(gi)007:2228: dga' ba'i gdong gi grogs byed ma //
NK033(gi)007:2229: 'dod khams gtso mo dbang du sdud //
NK033(gi)007:2230: khyod ni ma brgyad gtso mo ste //
NK033(gi)007:2231: khrag bcud 'thung zhing dgra bo gsod //
NK033(gi)007:2232: dam rdzas brgyan gyi gtor ma longs //
NK033(gi)007:2233: khrag nad 'phen zhing phrin las mdzod //
NK033(gi)007:2234: phrin las bdag mo mthu ma chung //
NK033(gi)007:2236: gtor ma dgra phyogs su 'phen zhing /
NK033(gi)007:2237: dmod mo gdab cing dmod bcol bya'o //
NK033(gi)007:2238: rjes su lha gshegs shing dkyil 'khor bsdu ba sogs rjes spyod spyi dang mthun no //
NK033(gi)007:2239: zhes pa 'adi'ang rgyal ba zhang ston gyis gter nas spyan drangs pa'i khros ma'i rgyud las btus te /
NK033(gi)007:2240: rdzogs chen pa 'od gsal sgyu ma gter bzhad rtsal gyis //
NK033(gi)007:2241: chu rta lo cho 'phrul chen po'i yar tshes brgyad
NK033(gi)007:2242: la bkod pa'i yi ge pa ni zangs brag gi
NK033(gi)007:2243: bla ma 'od gsal tshul khrims kyis bgyis pa'o //
NK033(gi)007:2244: rgyud bcu bdun gyi dbang 'di la /
NK033(gi)007:2245: rnam 'joms khrus dbang dang zhi ba'i dbang gcig /
NK033(gi)007:2247: tshe dbang rin po che dang gsum /
NK033(gi)007:2248: rig pa rang gi dbang bskur ba dang bzhi /
NK033(gi)007:2249: bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang dang lnga /
NK033(gi)007:2251: rdzogs chen rang snang gi dbang dang /
NK033(gi)007:2252: 'khor lo rin po che sku ltar 'bar ba'i dbang
NK033(gi)007:2253: gcig ste bdun po de la thog ma nas sa
NK033(gi)007:2254: bcad mdzad 'dug pa'i stabs kyis blo chung dag mgo
NK033(gi)007:2255: rmongs kyis dogs nas 'dir tho tsam bkod pa ste
NK033(gi)007:2256: / rgyas par gzhung dang sa bcad bsgrigs nas shes par bya'o //
